Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.23,1:23:44.32,english,,0,0,0,,Notice the little text box below the cat is asking, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.23,1:23:44.32,chinese,,0,0,0,,注意猫角色下方的文本框正在询问："你叫什么名字？"
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.32,1:23:46.59,english,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to type in D-A-V-I-D and hit Enter.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.32,1:23:46.59,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以我要输入D-A-V-I-D并按回车键。
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.59,1:23:48.12,english,,0,0,0,,Or I can click the blue check.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.59,1:23:48.12,chinese,,0,0,0,,或者我可以点击蓝色的勾号。
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.12,1:23:50.31,english,,0,0,0,,Enter.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.31,1:23:51.80,english,,0,0,0,,OK, it's a little weird.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.31,1:23:51.80,chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧，这有点奇怪。
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.80,1:23:53.76,english,,0,0,0,,I wanted him to say, "hello," not just my name.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.80,1:23:53.76,chinese,,0,0,0,,我想让他说 "你好"，而不仅仅是我的名字。
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.76,1:23:55.02,english,,0,0,0,,So let me Stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.76,1:23:55.02,chinese,,0,0,0,,停停。
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.02,1:23:56.19,english,,0,0,0,,Let me start it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.02,1:23:56.19,chinese,,0,0,0,,重新开始。
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.19,1:23:57.64,english,,0,0,0,,All right, hello, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.19,1:23:57.64,chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧，你好，你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.64,1:24:00.23,english,,0,0,0,,D-A-V-I-D. Enter.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.23,1:24:02.49,english,,0,0,0,,Huh-- kind of rude.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.23,1:24:02.49,chinese,,0,0,0,,啊... 有点没礼貌。
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.49,1:24:04.89,english,,0,0,0,,Why is there this bug?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.49,1:24:04.89,chinese,,0,0,0,,为什么会出现这个bug？
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.89,1:24:07.92,english,,0,0,0,,Like, I wanted to say, "Hello, David," not just "David."
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.89,1:24:07.92,chinese,,0,0,0,,我想说 "你好，David"，而不只是 "David"。
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.92,1:24:11.55,english,,0,0,0,,And yet twice it has failed to do so.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.92,1:24:11.55,chinese,,0,0,0,,然而，它两次都没有做到这一点。
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.55,1:24:12.56,english,,0,0,0,,Yeah--
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.56,1:24:13.57,english,,0,0,0,,AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE]
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.57,1:24:17.65,english,,0,0,0,,DAVID J. MALAN: Yeah, the computer's processing my directions, my actions, really quickly.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.57,1:24:17.65,chinese,,0,0,0,,是的，电脑处理指令和行动真的特别快。
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.65,1:24:18.95,english,,0,0,0,,And so it actually is doing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.65,1:24:18.95,chinese,,0,0,0,,因此，它实际上是这样做的，先显示"Hello, "，很快切换到"David"。
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.95,1:24:23.22,english,,0,0,0,,It's just, you and I, in the room, are just way too slow to notice that it said-- (QUICKLY) "Hello, David."
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.95,1:24:23.22,chinese,,0,0,0,,只是，我们反应太慢，没注意到它说——"Hello, David."
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.22,1:24:25.47,english,,0,0,0,,It just seems to have just said, "David."
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.22,1:24:25.47,chinese,,0,0,0,,它似乎只说了 "David"。
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.47,1:24:26.91,english,,0,0,0,,So all right, how can I fix this?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.47,1:24:26.91,chinese,,0,0,0,,那么好吧，我该如何解决这个问题呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.91,1:24:29.94,english,,0,0,0,,Well, here's where you start to poke around and think about how you might solve this.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.91,1:24:29.94,chinese,,0,0,0,,好的，这时候你可以开始探索和思考如何解决问题。
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.94,1:24:31.10,english,,0,0,0,,Let me go back under Looks.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.94,1:24:31.10,chinese,,0,0,0,,让我回到外观类别。
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.10,1:24:33.33,english,,0,0,0,,Maybe there's a smarter way to do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.10,1:24:33.33,chinese,,0,0,0,,也许有一种更智能的方法来解决这个问题。
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.33,1:24:34.52,english,,0,0,0,,Maybe I could do--
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.33,1:24:34.52,chinese,,0,0,0,,也许我可以这样做——
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.52,1:24:35.54,english,,0,0,0,,OK, I could do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.52,1:24:35.54,chinese,,0,0,0,,好的，我可以这样做。
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.54,1:24:42.15,english,,0,0,0,,How about instead of just Say "hello," there's apparently another puzzle piece where I can time it so I can maybe slow things down a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.54,1:24:42.15,chinese,,0,0,0,,我要试试这样。我不仅要说 "hello"，还可以在两次说话之间加入一些时间间隔，以减慢速度。
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.15,1:24:43.11,english,,0,0,0,,So let me do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.15,1:24:43.11,chinese,,0,0,0,,试试这样做。
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.11,1:24:45.81,english,,0,0,0,,Let me throw away all of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.11,1:24:45.81,chinese,,0,0,0,,我要先删除掉之前的代码。
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.81,1:24:49.14,english,,0,0,0,,Let me drag a Say "hello" for 2 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.81,1:24:49.14,chinese,,0,0,0,,然后我拖拽一个 "Say hello for 2 seconds"
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.14,1:24:51.87,english,,0,0,0,,Let me drag another Say "hello" for 2 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.14,1:24:51.87,chinese,,0,0,0,,再拖拽另一个 "Say hello for 2 seconds"
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.87,1:24:54.50,english,,0,0,0,,Let me change the first one to, indeed, "hello" comma.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.87,1:24:54.50,chinese,,0,0,0,,我要把第一个拼图块里的文本改为 "hello，"。
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.50,1:24:57.53,english,,0,0,0,,And then let me go back to Sensing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.50,1:24:57.53,chinese,,0,0,0,,然后我回到感知类别，
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.53,1:25:01.46,english,,0,0,0,,Let me grab that same answer because I threw it away a second ago, and I'll just change it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.53,1:25:01.46,chinese,,0,0,0,,再次拖拽那个返回值 answer，因为我之前把它删除了，\N现在我只需要修改一下文本就可以了，
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.46,1:25:02.96,english,,0,0,0,,I don't even have to delete "hello."
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.46,1:25:02.96,chinese,,0,0,0,,我甚至不用删除 "hello"。
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.96,1:25:04.74,english,,0,0,0,,I can just overwrite it like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.96,1:25:04.74,chinese,,0,0,0,,覆盖掉就可以。
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.74,1:25:08.36,english,,0,0,0,,So now I think we'll kind of pump the brakes and see things more slowly.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.74,1:25:08.36,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以，现在我们踩下了刹车，可以慢点来。
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.36,1:25:09.62,english,,0,0,0,,Let me Stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.36,1:25:09.62,chinese,,0,0,0,,先停下来。
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.62,1:25:10.55,english,,0,0,0,,Let me start.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.62,1:25:10.55,chinese,,0,0,0,,重新开始。
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.55,1:25:12.05,english,,0,0,0,,D-A-V-I-D, Enter.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.55,1:25:12.05,chinese,,0,0,0,,D-A-V-I-D，回车。
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.05,1:25:14.60,english,,0,0,0,,Hello, David.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.60,1:25:18.12,english,,0,0,0,,OK, so it's better, like it seems to be working.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.60,1:25:18.12,chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧，现在好多了，起作用了。
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.12,1:25:21.25,english,,0,0,0,,I think your hypothesis was right, just looks kind of stupid, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.12,1:25:21.25,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们的设想没问题，只是看起来有点呆是吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.25,1:25:22.88,english,,0,0,0,,Like, the fact that it's saying Hello--
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.25,1:25:22.88,chinese,,0,0,0,,就像它在说 "你好...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.88,1:25:24.17,english,,0,0,0,,[PAUSE]
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.17,1:25:25.64,english,,0,0,0,,--David, like we can do better.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.17,1:25:25.64,chinese,,0,0,0,,...David" ，我们可以做好点。
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.64,1:25:29.93,english,,0,0,0,,And like, literally every piece of software on your phone or Mac or PC is better than that.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.64,1:25:29.93,chinese,,0,0,0,,而且，你手机、Mac 或 PC 上的每款软件都比它好。
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.93,1:25:33.75,english,,0,0,0,,It adds words together in the user interfaces you and I are familiar with.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.93,1:25:33.75,chinese,,0,0,0,,它通过我们熟悉的用户界面将单词拼接在一起。
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.75,1:25:35.48,english,,0,0,0,,So let's go a little more fishing here.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.75,1:25:35.48,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以，让我们在这里再多思考一会儿。
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.48,1:25:36.95,english,,0,0,0,,Let me throw away these.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.48,1:25:36.95,chinese,,0,0,0,,扔掉这些先。
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.95,1:25:39.86,english,,0,0,0,,Let me go back to Looks and just get the simpler Say.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.95,1:25:39.86,chinese,,0,0,0,,回到 "外观"，抓起 Say 函数。
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.86,1:25:45.72,english,,0,0,0,,I want this to say, "Hello" comma name, where name comes from that Answer return value.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.86,1:25:45.72,chinese,,0,0,0,,我想让它说 "Hello, " name，其中 name 来自 Answer 的返回值。
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.72,1:25:46.74,english,,0,0,0,,So how can I do this?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.72,1:25:46.74,chinese,,0,0,0,,那么，我该怎么做呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.74,1:25:49.44,english,,0,0,0,,Well, let me go under Operations, which we haven't been before.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.74,1:25:49.44,chinese,,0,0,0,,好的，打开 Operations（运算）类别，这是我们以前没有接触过的。
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.44,1:25:50.73,english,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of stuff in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.44,1:25:50.73,chinese,,0,0,0,,这里有很多东西。
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.73,1:25:53.72,english,,0,0,0,,Some of it's mathematically related, adding, subtracting, and so forth.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.73,1:25:53.72,chinese,,0,0,0,,有些与数学相关，例如加法、减法等等。
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.72,1:25:56.28,english,,0,0,0,,You can generate random numbers which might be useful.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.72,1:25:56.28,chinese,,0,0,0,,你可以生成随机数，这可能会有用。
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.28,1:25:59.81,english,,0,0,0,,And if I keep scrolling down, there's this Join "apple" and "banana."
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.28,1:25:59.81,chinese,,0,0,0,,如果我继续向下滚动，会找到一个拼图块，叫做 Join "apple" and "banana"。
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.81,1:26:01.28,english,,0,0,0,,But that's just placeholder text.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.81,1:26:01.28,chinese,,0,0,0,,但这只是占位符文本。
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.28,1:26:06.17,english,,0,0,0,,You can join one piece of text with another piece of text, by default "apple" and "banana."
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.28,1:26:06.17,chinese,,0,0,0,,你可以将一段文本与另一段文本连接起来，默认情况下是"apple"和"banana"。
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.17,1:26:08.48,english,,0,0,0,,But let's change it to "hello" and my name.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.17,1:26:08.48,chinese,,0,0,0,,但让我们把它改成"hello"和我的名字。
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.48,1:26:11.12,english,,0,0,0,,So this, too, wrong size but right shape.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.48,1:26:11.12,chinese,,0,0,0,,这也是正确的形状，但是大小不对。
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.12,1:26:13.19,english,,0,0,0,,So let me let it snap into place.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.12,1:26:13.19,chinese,,0,0,0,,让我把它吸附到合适的位置。
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.19,1:26:15.92,english,,0,0,0,,Let me go ahead now and do "hello" comma.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.19,1:26:15.92,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在让我继续输入 "hello，"。
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.92,1:26:20.84,english,,0,0,0,,And now I think I just want to go grab that Answer return value.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.92,1:26:20.84,chinese,,0,0,0,,然后我想要去获取那个返回值 answer 。
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.84,1:26:25.28,english,,0,0,0,,Let me drag the same oval as before, clobber-- that is, overwrite-- banana.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.84,1:26:25.28,chinese,,0,0,0,,让我拖拽之前相同的椭圆，覆盖掉 "banana"。
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.28,1:26:28.43,english,,0,0,0,,So now I'm kind of composing functions.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.28,1:26:28.43,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以现在我正在组合函数。
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.43,1:26:33.97,english,,0,0,0,,The output of one function, Join, is going to be the input of another function, Say.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.43,1:26:33.97,chinese,,0,0,0,,一个函数 Join 的输出将成为另一个函数 Say 的输入。
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.97,1:26:38.66,english,,0,0,0,,So let's see what happens now that they're kind of stacked on top of each other or nested, so to speak.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.97,1:26:38.66,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在让我们看看它们彼此堆叠或者说嵌套在一起之后会发生什么。
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.66,1:26:42.44,english,,0,0,0,,Click the Green Flag, D-A-V-I-D. Enter.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.66,1:26:42.44,chinese,,0,0,0,,点击绿旗，D-A-V-I-D。回车。
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.44,1:26:43.35,english,,0,0,0,,"Hello, David."
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.35,1:26:44.69,english,,0,0,0,,All right, that was pretty fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.35,1:26:44.69,chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧，这也太快了。
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.69,1:26:45.68,english,,0,0,0,,Let's just do it once more.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.69,1:26:45.68,chinese,,0,0,0,,让我们再来一次。
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.68,1:26:46.31,english,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.31,1:26:47.27,english,,0,0,0,,Start.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.27,1:26:49.54,english,,0,0,0,,Here we go, D-A-V-I-D. Enter.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.27,1:26:49.54,chinese,,0,0,0,,点击绿旗，D-A-V-I-D。回车。
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.54,1:26:50.04,english,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.04,1:26:52.65,english,,0,0,0,,All right, it's not the most exciting program in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.04,1:26:52.65,chinese,,0,0,0,,好的，这可能不是世界上最激动人心的程序。
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.65,1:26:53.75,english,,0,0,0,,But it's more correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.65,1:26:53.75,chinese,,0,0,0,,但它更加正确，
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.75,1:26:57.06,english,,0,0,0,,It's better designed just because that's what you would kind of expect the software to do
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.75,1:26:57.06,chinese,,0,0,0,,它设计得更好，因为这是你期望软件能做的事情，
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.06,1:27:03.96,english,,0,0,0,,and not be some kind of lame user interface that's just inserting random delays to just make it kind of work, like that's a workaround, a hack, if you will.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.06,1:27:03.96,chinese,,0,0,0,,而不是一些仅仅通过插入随机延迟来使它“大概工作”的可怜用户界面，\N这样只是一种变通，一种权宜之计，你可以这样说。
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.96,1:27:06.17,english,,0,0,0,,But there's some cool things you can do with Scratch.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.96,1:27:06.17,chinese,,0,0,0,,不过，用 Scratch 也能做一些很酷的事情。
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.17,1:27:10.94,english,,0,0,0,,And we won't really go down the rabbit hole of all of the fun and family-friendly features that it has.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.17,1:27:10.94,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们不会深入探讨所有有趣的功能。
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.94,1:27:12.81,english,,0,0,0,,But there is one that's kind of cool here.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.94,1:27:12.81,chinese,,0,0,0,,但有一个功能还是挺酷的。
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.81,1:27:16.55,english,,0,0,0,,Let me go into the Extensions button at the bottom left of my screen.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.81,1:27:16.55,chinese,,0,0,0,,让我点击屏幕左下角的 "Extensions" 按钮。
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.55,1:27:17.72,english,,0,0,0,,And this one's kind of cool.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.55,1:27:17.72,chinese,,0,0,0,,这个还挺酷的。
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.72,1:27:19.57,english,,0,0,0,,Let me go to Text to Speech.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.72,1:27:19.57,chinese,,0,0,0,,我选择"Text to Speech"。
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.57,1:27:22.70,english,,0,0,0,,And you'll notice that this one requires internet because it's cloud based.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.57,1:27:22.70,chinese,,0,0,0,,你会注意到这个功能需要互联网，因为它是基于云的。
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.70,1:27:27.71,english,,0,0,0,,But this just gave me some new puzzle pieces in a new category,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.70,1:27:27.71,chinese,,0,0,0,,但是这给我提供了一些新的拼图块，属于一个新的类别，
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.71,1:27:28.34,english,,0,0,0,,Text to Speech.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.71,1:27:28.34,chinese,,0,0,0,,名为 "文字转语音"。
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.34,1:27:30.71,english,,0,0,0,,And these green ones do exactly what they say.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.34,1:27:30.71,chinese,,0,0,0,,这些绿色的拼图块做的就是它们名字里面写的。
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.71,1:27:31.86,english,,0,0,0,,So let me do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.71,1:27:31.86,chinese,,0,0,0,,那就让我来吧。
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.86,1:27:33.12,english,,0,0,0,,Let me zoom out again.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.86,1:27:33.12,chinese,,0,0,0,,再次缩小视图。
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.12,1:27:34.54,english,,0,0,0,,Let me keep the Join block.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.12,1:27:34.54,chinese,,0,0,0,,我保留Join拼图块，
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.54,1:27:36.71,english,,0,0,0,,And I'm just going to temporarily toss it over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.54,1:27:36.71,chinese,,0,0,0,,但暂时把它放在这里。
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.71,1:27:40.07,english,,0,0,0,,It's not going to delete itself because I didn't drag it over to the other side.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.71,1:27:40.07,chinese,,0,0,0,,它不会自己删除，因为我没有把它拖到另一边。
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.07,1:27:42.80,english,,0,0,0,,But I'm going to get rid of the Say block, in purple.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.07,1:27:42.80,chinese,,0,0,0,,但是我要删除紫色的 Say 拼图块。
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.80,1:27:47.57,english,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do the Speak block here, in green, and let it snap into place.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.80,1:27:47.57,chinese,,0,0,0,,我在这里用绿色的 Speak 拼图块替换它，并让它吸附到合适的位置。
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.57,1:27:50.99,english,,0,0,0,,And then I'm going to drag and drop this onto the input to Speak.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.57,1:27:50.99,chinese,,0,0,0,,然后我要将这个返回值 Answer 拼图块拖放到 Speak 的输入上。
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.99,1:27:54.29,english,,0,0,0,,And now, perhaps a little more adorably, let's try this.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.99,1:27:54.29,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在，也许会更加可爱一些，我们来试一下。
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.29,1:27:56.27,english,,0,0,0,,Green Flag, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.29,1:27:56.27,chinese,,0,0,0,,点击绿旗，出现 "你叫什么名字？"
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.27,1:27:57.71,english,,0,0,0,,D-A-V-I-D. Enter.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.27,1:27:57.71,chinese,,0,0,0,,D-A-V-I-D，回车。
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.71,1:27:58.46,english,,0,0,0,,And--
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.46,1:28:00.57,english,,0,0,0,,COMPUTER: Hello, David.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.57,1:28:01.37,english,,0,0,0,,DAVID J. MALAN: OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.57,1:28:01.37,chinese,,0,0,0,,大卫-J-马兰：好的。
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.37,1:28:02.37,english,,0,0,0,,[LAUGHTER]
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.37,1:28:03.89,english,,0,0,0,,It's a little robotic.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.37,1:28:03.89,chinese,,0,0,0,,有点像机器人。
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.89,1:28:05.91,english,,0,0,0,,But at least now it has synthesized speech.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.89,1:28:05.91,chinese,,0,0,0,,但至少现在有了合成语音。
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.91,1:28:13.55,english,,0,0,0,,And I've kind of got my own, like, Siri or Google Assistant or Alexa thing going on here now, where it's now recognized whatever text it is, and it's played it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.91,1:28:13.55,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在我们有了 Siri 或 Google Assistant 或 Alexa，可以识别文字并播放出来。
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.55,1:28:17.48,english,,0,0,0,,Well, let's make this an actual cat that doesn't talk in that weird human voice.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.55,1:28:17.48,chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧，让我们把它变成一只真正的猫，它不会用那种奇怪的人类声音说话。
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.48,1:28:19.61,english,,0,0,0,,Let me go ahead and get rid of most of this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.48,1:28:19.61,chinese,,0,0,0,,让我删除大部分东西。
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.61,1:28:22.73,english,,0,0,0,,And let's get the cat to actually meow, like a cat tends to.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.61,1:28:22.73,chinese,,0,0,0,,让这只猫像猫一样喵喵叫吧。
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.73,1:28:24.65,english,,0,0,0,,And let me go under the Sounds block.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.73,1:28:24.65,chinese,,0,0,0,,让我进入声音类别。
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.65,1:28:33.08,english,,0,0,0,,Now MIT gives you a few sounds for free because it's designed around a cat, by default. And I'm going to go ahead and grab this one, Play Sound Meow until done.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.65,1:28:33.08,chinese,,0,0,0,,MIT 为你提供了一些免费的声音，因为它默认设计是围绕一只猫的。\N我要选择这个，播放猫叫声直到结束。
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.08,1:28:36.86,english,,0,0,0,,And now-- and we heard a teaser for this earlier in the crowd--
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.08,1:28:36.86,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在—— 刚才就听到有人在下面跟着喵了。
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.86,1:28:38.98,english,,0,0,0,,[MEOW]
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.98,1:28:40.44,english,,0,0,0,,It's a little piercing, admittedly.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.98,1:28:40.44,chinese,,0,0,0,,这听起来可能有点刺耳。
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.44,1:28:42.46,english,,0,0,0,,Maybe we can lower the volume a little bit there.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.44,1:28:42.46,chinese,,0,0,0,,或许我们可以把音量降低一点。
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.46,1:28:45.71,english,,0,0,0,,But notice, if I want the cat to meow a second time, I'll just click it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.46,1:28:45.71,chinese,,0,0,0,,但请注意，如果我想让猫再喵喵叫一次，我就再点击一次。
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.71,1:28:46.90,english,,0,0,0,,[MEOW]
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.90,1:28:48.69,english,,0,0,0,,OK, and over there, too, I hear--
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.90,1:28:48.69,chinese,,0,0,0,,好的，大家能听见——
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.69,1:28:50.32,english,,0,0,0,,[MEOW]
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.32,1:28:50.82,english,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.82,1:28:51.32,english,,0,0,0,,[MEOW]
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.32,1:28:53.50,english,,0,0,0,,All right, so it's kind of cute now, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.32,1:28:53.50,chinese,,0,0,0,,是吧，现在有点可爱了吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.50,1:28:54.96,english,,0,0,0,,So it's just meow--
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.50,1:28:54.96,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以，它只是喵，
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.96,1:28:56.61,english,,0,0,0,,OK, yes, echo, echo.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.96,1:28:56.61,chinese,,0,0,0,,对对，有回声。
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.61,1:28:59.76,english,,0,0,0,,So it's meowing now every time I hit the Green Flag.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.61,1:28:59.76,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以现在每次我点绿旗的时候，它都会喵喵叫。
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.76,1:29:02.10,english,,0,0,0,,Now, that's great, but even a kid is probably going to--
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.76,1:29:02.10,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在很不错， 不过可能会想，
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.10,1:29:02.73,english,,0,0,0,,[MEOW]
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.73,1:29:03.78,english,,0,0,0,,--like would prefer that it--
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.73,1:29:03.78,chinese,,0,0,0,,希望它可以，
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.78,1:29:03.84,english,,0,0,0,,[MEOW]
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.84,1:29:06.79,english,,0,0,0,,--just meow, perhaps, like again and again, without having to keep--
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.84,1:29:06.79,chinese,,0,0,0,,就 "喵喵 "地叫，一次又一次，而不必每次都要，
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.79,1:29:07.29,english,,0,0,0,,[MEOW]
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.29,1:29:08.16,english,,0,0,0,,--hitting the button.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.29,1:29:08.16,chinese,,0,0,0,,按下按钮。
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.16,1:29:09.88,english,,0,0,0,,So how might we do this?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.16,1:29:09.88,chinese,,0,0,0,,那么，我们该如何做呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.88,1:29:16.57,english,,0,0,0,,All right, well, if I want it to meow multiple times, why don't I just, like, grab it another time and another time?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.88,1:29:16.57,chinese,,0,0,0,,好的，如果我想让它叫多次，为什么我不直接再拖拽一次、再拖拽一次呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.57,1:29:21.72,english,,0,0,0,,Alternatively, you can Right-click or Control-click a puzzle piece and just duplicate it from a little menu that drops down.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.57,1:29:21.72,chinese,,0,0,0,,或者，你可以右键点击或者按住Control键点击拼图块，\N然后从弹出的菜单中选择"Duplicate"，复制。
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.72,1:29:22.92,english,,0,0,0,,So here we go, three meows.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.72,1:29:22.92,chinese,,0,0,0,,好了，现在是三声喵。
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.92,1:29:25.09,english,,0,0,0,,[MEOWING]
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.96,1:29:27.73,english,,0,0,0,,All right, that's not really a happy cat.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.96,1:29:27.73,chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧，听起来小猫不太开心。
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.73,1:29:29.20,english,,0,0,0,,It sounds maybe hungry.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.73,1:29:29.20,chinese,,0,0,0,,它是不是有点饿了。
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.20,1:29:31.24,english,,0,0,0,,So can we slow that down?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.20,1:29:31.24,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以我们能不能让它喵得慢一点呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.24,1:29:32.38,english,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.24,1:29:32.38,chinese,,0,0,0,,嗯，也许可以。
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.38,1:29:34.63,english,,0,0,0,,In fact, if I poke around, let me go under Control.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.38,1:29:34.63,chinese,,0,0,0,,如果我四处翻找，进入控制类别。
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.63,1:29:36.85,english,,0,0,0,,It looks like there's a Wait block.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.63,1:29:36.85,chinese,,0,0,0,,看起来有一个等待拼图块。
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.85,1:29:40.63,english,,0,0,0,,Wait 1 Second, by default. And notice, Scratch will be pretty accommodating.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.85,1:29:40.63,chinese,,0,0,0,,默认情况下等待 1 秒。请注意，Scratch 会很通情达理。
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.63,1:29:44.41,english,,0,0,0,,If you just hover in between blocks, it will grow to fill that too.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.63,1:29:44.41,chinese,,0,0,0,,如果你将鼠标悬停在两个拼图块之间，它也会自动填进去。
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.41,1:29:47.09,english,,0,0,0,,So I could change it to 1 or 2 or anything, seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.41,1:29:47.09,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以我可以将等待时间更改为 1 秒、2 秒或其他任何时间。
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.09,1:29:48.97,english,,0,0,0,,I'll just leave it at the default for now, 1.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.09,1:29:48.97,chinese,,0,0,0,,我暂时将其保留默认值 1 秒。
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.97,1:29:50.68,english,,0,0,0,,And now I'll go ahead and do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.97,1:29:50.68,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在，我要跑一下看看效果。
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.68,1:29:52.83,english,,0,0,0,,[MEOWING]
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.58,1:29:58.79,english,,0,0,0,,OK, so cuter and less hungry and just more friendly.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.58,1:29:58.79,chinese,,0,0,0,,好了，更可爱、更不饿、更友好了。
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.79,1:30:00.74,english,,0,0,0,,But this isn't the best design.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.79,1:30:00.74,chinese,,0,0,0,,但这并不是最好的设计。
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.74,1:30:01.46,english,,0,0,0,,It is correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.74,1:30:01.46,chinese,,0,0,0,,它当然正确。
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.46,1:30:02.96,english,,0,0,0,,And let's use that as a term of art.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.46,1:30:02.96,chinese,,0,0,0,,让我们把它作为一个艺术术语来看待。
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.96,1:30:05.72,english,,0,0,0,,Correct means the code does what you want it to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.96,1:30:05.72,chinese,,0,0,0,,正确的意思是代码能按照你的意愿执行。
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.72,1:30:08.09,english,,0,0,0,,I want the cat to meow three times slowly.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.72,1:30:08.09,chinese,,0,0,0,,我想让猫慢慢地喵叫三声，
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.09,1:30:08.72,english,,0,0,0,,And it did.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.09,1:30:08.72,chinese,,0,0,0,,它确实做到了。
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.72,1:30:10.37,english,,0,0,0,,So I'd wager this is correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.72,1:30:10.37,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以我可以说这是正确的。
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.37,1:30:12.38,english,,0,0,0,,But it's not the best design.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.37,1:30:12.38,chinese,,0,0,0,,但这并不是最佳设计。
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.38,1:30:14.81,english,,0,0,0,,And this is where things get more subjective, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.38,1:30:14.81,chinese,,0,0,0,,这里就涉及到更主观的因素，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.81,1:30:20.66,english,,0,0,0,,Like, you could write accurate sentences in an essay for an English class, but otherwise, it's just completely a mess.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.81,1:30:20.66,chinese,,0,0,0,,就像你可以在英语课的论文中写出准确的句子，但总体来说它可能是一团糟。
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.66,1:30:24.83,english,,0,0,0,,Like, your arguments here and there, and you don't say anything wrong, but you don't say it well.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.66,1:30:24.83,chinese,,0,0,0,,你的论据到处都是，虽然没有错误，但表达得不好。
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.83,1:30:28.11,english,,0,0,0,,In the context of code, we can do better than this.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.83,1:30:28.11,chinese,,0,0,0,,在编程中，我们可以做得更好。
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.11,1:30:32.34,english,,0,0,0,,And Copy/Paste or repeating yourself again and again tends to be bad practice.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.11,1:30:32.34,chinese,,0,0,0,,而复制/粘贴或者一遍又一遍重复自己往往是不好的做法。
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.34,1:30:32.84,english,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.84,1:30:37.18,english,,0,0,0,,Suppose that you want to change the Wait to 2 seconds instead of 1.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.84,1:30:37.18,chinese,,0,0,0,,假设你想将等待时间从 1 秒改为 2 秒。
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.18,1:30:38.48,english,,0,0,0,,It's admittedly not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.18,1:30:38.48,chinese,,0,0,0,,这确实不是什么很难的问题。
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.48,1:30:40.40,english,,0,0,0,,Fine, I click there, I change it to 2.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.48,1:30:40.40,chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧，我点击那里，将它改成 2 秒。
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.40,1:30:41.99,english,,0,0,0,,I click there, I change it to 2.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.40,1:30:41.99,chinese,,0,0,0,,我点击那里，将其改为 2 秒。
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.99,1:30:43.82,english,,0,0,0,,But what if you meow 5 times, 10 times?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.99,1:30:43.82,chinese,,0,0,0,,但如果有 5 次、10 次猫叫呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.82,1:30:46.85,english,,0,0,0,,Now I have to change the Wait, like, in 5, 10 different places.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.82,1:30:46.85,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在我必须在 5 个、10 个不同的地方改变等待时间。
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.85,1:30:47.90,english,,0,0,0,,Like, that's just stupid.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.85,1:30:47.90,chinese,,0,0,0,,这实在很愚蠢。
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.90,1:30:53.27,english,,0,0,0,,It's taking unnecessary human time, and you're going to screw up eventually, especially if your program is getting longer.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.90,1:30:53.27,chinese,,0,0,0,,这浪费了不必要的时间，而且你最终会出错，特别是当你的程序变得更长时。
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.27,1:30:54.74,english,,0,0,0,,You're going to miss one of the inputs.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.27,1:30:54.74,chinese,,0,0,0,,你会漏改掉其中一个，
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.74,1:30:56.36,english,,0,0,0,,You're going to leave the number wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.74,1:30:56.36,chinese,,0,0,0,,或者将数字填错。
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.36,1:30:57.08,english,,0,0,0,,And that's a bug.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.36,1:30:57.08,chinese,,0,0,0,,就会出现 bug，正确性也没了。
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.08,1:31:04.05,english,,0,0,0,,So just based on what you've seen already or if you've program before, which a few of you have, what's the term of art here that will solve this?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.08,1:31:04.05,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以基于你已经见过的或者你以前的编程经验，你知道应该用什么术语来解决这个问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.05,1:31:06.09,english,,0,0,0,,How can we design this better?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.05,1:31:06.09,chinese,,0,0,0,,如何才能设计得更好？
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.09,1:31:07.23,english,,0,0,0,,AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE]
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.23,1:31:08.56,english,,0,0,0,,DAVID J. MALAN: I heard it here.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.23,1:31:08.56,chinese,,0,0,0,,我听到啦。
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.56,1:31:12.11,english,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so a loop-- a loop, some kind of cycle that says, do that again.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.56,1:31:12.11,chinese,,0,0,0,,是的，所以用循环—— 一个循环，也就是说，再来一次。
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.11,1:31:16.43,english,,0,0,0,,Do that again-- not infinitely many times, necessarily, but some finite number.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.11,1:31:16.43,chinese,,0,0,0,,再做一次—— 不会是无限次，一定是有限次。
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.43,1:31:18.74,english,,0,0,0,,Well, you can perhaps see a spoiler on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.43,1:31:18.74,chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧，你也许在屏幕上看到剧透了。
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.74,1:31:22.76,english,,0,0,0,,Under the same orange Control category is a Repeat block.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.74,1:31:22.76,chinese,,0,0,0,,就在橙色控制类别下有一个 Repeat 拼图。
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.76,1:31:24.32,english,,0,0,0,,And by default, it's proposing 10.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.76,1:31:24.32,chinese,,0,0,0,,默认情况下，它设置为 10。
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.32,1:31:25.44,english,,0,0,0,,But we can change that.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.32,1:31:25.44,chinese,,0,0,0,,但我们可以改一改。
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.44,1:31:26.28,english,,0,0,0,,So let me do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.44,1:31:26.28,chinese,,0,0,0,,来试试吧。
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.28,1:31:29.93,english,,0,0,0,,I'm going to throw away most of this Copy/Paste as redundant.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.28,1:31:29.93,chinese,,0,0,0,,我打算把这些复制/粘贴的大部分内容当作多余的东西扔掉。
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.93,1:31:33.47,english,,0,0,0,,I'm going to detach this temporarily just to make room for something else.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.93,1:31:33.47,chinese,,0,0,0,,把这个暂时拆开，腾出地方放点别的。
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.47,1:31:37.59,english,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to drag a Repeat block over here and let that snap into place.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.47,1:31:37.59,chinese,,0,0,0,,我要把一个 Repeat 块拖到这里，让它就位。
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.59,1:31:40.34,english,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to change it for now, just to be 3, for consistency.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.59,1:31:40.34,chinese,,0,0,0,,和刚才保持统一，我暂时把它改成 3。
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.34,1:31:44.66,english,,0,0,0,,And this is the correct shape even though it's too small, but Scratch will accommodate that for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.34,1:31:44.66,chinese,,0,0,0,,形状正确，尽管有点小，但 Scratch 会自动调整。
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.66,1:31:50.37,english,,0,0,0,,And now-- same output but arguably better designed.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.66,1:31:50.37,chinese,,0,0,0,,而现在—— 尽管输出一致，不过可以说设计得更好。
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.37,1:31:50.87,english,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.87,1:31:55.04,english,,0,0,0,,Because if I want to change the number of meows, I change it in one place, no Copy/Paste messiness.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.87,1:31:55.04,chinese,,0,0,0,,因为如果我想更改喵星人的数量，\N只需在一个地方进行更改即可，不会出现复制/粘贴的混乱情况。
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.04,1:31:56.86,english,,0,0,0,,If I want to change the waiting, one place.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.04,1:31:56.86,chinese,,0,0,0,,如果我想改变等待时间，也只改一个地方。
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.86,1:31:59.45,english,,0,0,0,,I don't have to change it in multiple places and not screw up.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.86,1:31:59.45,chinese,,0,0,0,,我不用在多个地方进行更改，更不会搞砸。
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.45,1:32:00.92,english,,0,0,0,,So let me hit the Green Flag.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.45,1:32:00.92,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以，让我点一下绿旗吧。
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.92,1:32:03.40,english,,0,0,0,,[MEOWING]
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.89,1:32:06.94,english,,0,0,0,,All right, so-- nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.89,1:32:06.94,chinese,,0,0,0,,嗯，很棒。
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.94,1:32:12.97,english,,0,0,0,,Now, it would have been nice if MIT had just given us a meow block that just automates all of this for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.94,1:32:12.97,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在，如果麻省理工学院能给我们一个喵的拼图块，\N让我们自动完成所有这些工作，那该多好啊。
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.97,1:32:15.91,english,,0,0,0,,Let me wager, they gave us the low-level implementation details.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.97,1:32:15.91,chinese,,0,0,0,,可以确定的是，他们帮我们实现了低层次的实施细节。
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.91,1:32:18.40,english,,0,0,0,,They gave us the Play Sound Meow.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.91,1:32:18.40,chinese,,0,0,0,,他们给了我们 Play Sound Meow 函数。
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.40,1:32:23.12,english,,0,0,0,,But I had to implement a decent number of blocks just to get a cat to meow again and again.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.40,1:32:23.12,chinese,,0,0,0,,但是，为了让一只猫一次又一次地 "喵喵喵" 叫，我还不得不组合很多拼图。
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.12,1:32:26.35,english,,0,0,0,,I feel like we should have gotten that for free from MIT.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.12,1:32:26.35,chinese,,0,0,0,,我觉得 MIT 该做出来让我们白嫖。
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.35,1:32:30.10,english,,0,0,0,,Well, they don't have to be the only ones that invent blocks for us to use.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.35,1:32:30.10,chinese,,0,0,0,,其实，并不是只有他们发明的函数块才能让我们使用。
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.10,1:32:33.92,english,,0,0,0,,You can write your own functions, your own verbs or actions.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.10,1:32:33.92,chinese,,0,0,0,,你可以自己写函数、动词或动作。
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.92,1:32:35.18,english,,0,0,0,,So how can we do this?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.92,1:32:35.18,chinese,,0,0,0,,那么，我们如何才能做到这一点呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.18,1:32:42.65,english,,0,0,0,,Let's make our own puzzle piece, called Meow, that uses this code but creates it in such a way that it's reusable elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.18,1:32:42.65,chinese,,0,0,0,,让我们自己制作一个名为 Meow 的拼图块，\N它使用了刚才的代码，但这样创建使它可以在其他地方重复使用。
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.65,1:32:43.42,english,,0,0,0,,So let me do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.65,1:32:43.42,chinese,,0,0,0,,来吧。
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.42,1:32:48.31,english,,0,0,0,,Under my blocks in pink here, I'm going to go ahead and click, literally, Make a Block.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.42,1:32:48.31,chinese,,0,0,0,,在粉红色的区块下，我要点击"制作区块"。
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.31,1:32:51.10,english,,0,0,0,,Now, here's an interface by which I can give the block a name.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.31,1:32:51.10,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在，这里有一个接口，我可以通过它给程序块命名。
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.10,1:32:53.41,english,,0,0,0,,M-E-O-W will be the name of this block.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.10,1:32:53.41,chinese,,0,0,0,,M-E-O-W 将是这个块的名称。
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.41,1:32:55.81,english,,0,0,0,,And I'm just going to go ahead and quickly click OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.41,1:32:55.81,chinese,,0,0,0,,我要点下"确定"。
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.81,1:33:06.71,english,,0,0,0,,That just gives me a very generic, pink puzzle piece that starts with the word Define because scratch is asking me to define, that is, implement or create, this new puzzle piece for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.81,1:33:06.71,chinese,,0,0,0,,那会给我一个非常通用的粉色拼图块，上面写着 "Define"，\N因为 Scratch 要求我定义，也就是实现或创建，这个新的拼图块。
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.71,1:33:08.05,english,,0,0,0,,Well, what does it mean to Meow?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.71,1:33:08.05,chinese,,0,0,0,,那么，这对 Meow块 意味着什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.05,1:33:14.89,english,,0,0,0,,I'm going to claim that it means to do these two steps, to play the sound meow and then just wait for 1 second.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.05,1:33:14.89,chinese,,0,0,0,,我要说这表示要执行这两个步骤，先播放声音 "meow"，然后等待 1 秒。
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.89,1:33:18.52,english,,0,0,0,,But what's powerful about this idea is look at this up top.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.89,1:33:18.52,chinese,,0,0,0,,但这个想法的强大之处在于，看看上面这个。
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.52,1:33:21.97,english,,0,0,0,,Now that I've made a block, it exists in Scratch.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.52,1:33:21.97,chinese,,0,0,0,,我创建了一个新的拼图块，它现在存在于 Scratch 中。
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.97,1:33:23.71,english,,0,0,0,,MIT didn't need to create this for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.97,1:33:23.71,chinese,,0,0,0,,MIT 不需要为我创建这个拼图块。
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.71,1:33:27.19,english,,0,0,0,,I created it for myself and even you, if we end up sharing code.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.71,1:33:27.19,chinese,,0,0,0,,我为自己创建了它，甚至为你创建了它，如果我们最终分享代码的话。
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.19,1:33:30.32,english,,0,0,0,,So I can now drag Meow up in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.19,1:33:30.32,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以我现在可以将 Meow 拖到这里。
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.32,1:33:35.68,english,,0,0,0,,And what's nice about Meow is that itself is, yes, a function, but it's also an abstraction.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.32,1:33:35.68,chinese,,0,0,0,,Meow 块的好处是它本身是一个函数，或者说一个抽象概念。
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.68,1:33:42.34,english,,0,0,0,,Like, never again do I or even you need to worry or care about what it means to meow or implement it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.68,1:33:42.34,chinese,,0,0,0,,以后我们再也不需要关心 Meow 的具体含义或者实现方式。
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.34,1:33:43.93,english,,0,0,0,,I can sort of drag it out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.34,1:33:43.93,chinese,,0,0,0,,我可以将它拖到一边，
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.93,1:33:45.79,english,,0,0,0,,I didn't delete it-- drag it out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.93,1:33:45.79,chinese,,0,0,0,,我没有删除它，只是将它拖到一边。
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.79,1:33:46.97,english,,0,0,0,,Out of sight, out of mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.79,1:33:46.97,chinese,,0,0,0,,眼不见，心不烦。
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.97,1:33:47.47,english,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.47,1:33:51.07,english,,0,0,0,,Because my code is now even better designed, in some sense, because it's more readable.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.47,1:33:51.07,chinese,,0,0,0,,这样我的代码设计得更棒了，易读性更好了。
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.07,1:33:51.91,english,,0,0,0,,What is it doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.07,1:33:51.91,chinese,,0,0,0,,它做了什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.91,1:33:55.00,english,,0,0,0,,When the Green Flag is clicked, repeat 3 times Meow.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.91,1:33:55.00,chinese,,0,0,0,,只要点击绿旗，就重复 3 次 "Meow"。
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.00,1:33:56.30,english,,0,0,0,,It just says what it means.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.00,1:33:56.30,chinese,,0,0,0,,这个函数名就是它干的事情。
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.30,1:34:03.04,english,,0,0,0,,And so it's a lot easier to read it, and it's a lot easier to think about it, especially if you're using Meow in other projects too.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.30,1:34:03.04,chinese,,0,0,0,,这样阅读起来就容易多了，思考起来也容易多了，\N尤其是当你在其他项目中也使用 Meow 函数的时候。
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.04,1:34:05.38,english,,0,0,0,,Now, let me go ahead and click Play.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.04,1:34:05.38,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在，我们点点播放。
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.38,1:34:06.28,english,,0,0,0,,[MEOW]
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.28,1:34:07.20,english,,0,0,0,,Same thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.28,1:34:07.20,chinese,,0,0,0,,是一样的。
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.20,1:34:07.70,english,,0,0,0,,[MEOW]
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.70,1:34:09.28,english,,0,0,0,,So it's not really fundamentally any different.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.70,1:34:09.28,chinese,,0,0,0,,因此，从根本上说并没有什么不同。
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.28,1:34:09.83,english,,0,0,0,,[MEOW]
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.83,1:34:15.01,english,,0,0,0,,But I can make this custom puzzle piece, this own function of mine, Meow, even more powerful.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.83,1:34:15.01,chinese,,0,0,0,,因为函数 Meow 是亲自写的，所以我们可以定制、修改，让它更加有用。
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.01,1:34:18.52,english,,0,0,0,,Let me kind of rewind a bit and go to my Meow puzzle piece.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.01,1:34:18.52,chinese,,0,0,0,,让我来倒带一下，看看 Meow 函数。
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.52,1:34:21.65,english,,0,0,0,,And I am going to Control-click or Right-click on my pink puzzle piece.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.52,1:34:21.65,chinese,,0,0,0,,我来按住 Control 键或右键单击我的粉色拼图。
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.65,1:34:22.70,english,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to edit it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.65,1:34:22.70,chinese,,0,0,0,,就可以编辑它。
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.70,1:34:25.21,english,,0,0,0,,So I kind of regret making Meow so simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.70,1:34:25.21,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以我有点后悔把 Meow 设计得这么简单。
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.21,1:34:31.96,english,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be nice if Meow took an input, a.k.a. an argument, that tells Meow how many times to meow.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.21,1:34:31.96,chinese,,0,0,0,,如果 Meow 能接受一个输入，也就是一个参数，\N告诉 Meow 要喵叫多少次，那该有多好。
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.96,1:34:34.30,english,,0,0,0,,Then I can get rid of that loop and just tell
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.96,1:34:34.30,chinese,,0,0,0,,那个循环就能丢掉了，只需要
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.30,1:34:36.53,english,,0,0,0,,Meow how many meows I actually want.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.30,1:34:36.53,chinese,,0,0,0,,告诉 Meow 我实际上想要多少声猫叫。
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.53,1:34:40.39,english,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to click on another button here called, literally, Add an Input.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.53,1:34:40.39,chinese,,0,0,0,,因此，我要点击这里的另一个按钮，字面意思是 "添加输入"。
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.39,1:34:42.08,english,,0,0,0,,And it's going to have placeholder here.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.39,1:34:42.08,chinese,,0,0,0,,这里会有一个占位符。
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.08,1:34:43.96,english,,0,0,0,,So I'm just going to put a placeholder there.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.08,1:34:43.96,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以我先在这里放一个占位符。
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.96,1:34:47.88,english,,0,0,0,,I keep using "n" for number, which is a go to in computer scientist terms.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.96,1:34:47.88,chinese,,0,0,0,,我一直用 "n "表示数字，我们计算机科学家都是这么约定俗成的。
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.88,1:34:52.03,english,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to add some descriptive text just so that it's a little more self-explanatory.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.88,1:34:52.03,chinese,,0,0,0,,我还要添加点描述性文字，让它更加一目了然。
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.03,1:34:54.07,english,,0,0,0,,I'm just going to say Meow n Times.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.03,1:34:54.07,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们想要的是让它喵 n 次。
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.07,1:34:55.51,english,,0,0,0,,But there's only one oval.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.07,1:34:55.51,chinese,,0,0,0,,其实只有这个椭圆形里的 n 是参数。
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.51,1:34:57.70,english,,0,0,0,,Times is just going to be explanatory text.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.51,1:34:57.70,chinese,,0,0,0,,times 只是解释性文字。
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.70,1:34:59.29,english,,0,0,0,,And now notice what has happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.70,1:34:59.29,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在注意看这里发生什么。
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.29,1:35:06.58,english,,0,0,0,,Now my puzzle piece takes an input, a.k.a. an argument, that will tell that function to meow some number of times.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.29,1:35:06.58,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在，这块拼图需要一个输入，也就是一个参数，这个参数会告诉函数喵喵叫多少次。
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.58,1:35:08.44,english,,0,0,0,,But it's not just going to work magically.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.58,1:35:08.44,chinese,,0,0,0,,但这没法神奇地自动生效。
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.44,1:35:11.11,english,,0,0,0,,I need to implement that lower level detail.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.44,1:35:11.11,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们需要实现较低级别的细节。
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.11,1:35:12.70,english,,0,0,0,,So let me zoom out.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.11,1:35:12.70,chinese,,0,0,0,,让我把镜头拉远。
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.70,1:35:14.91,english,,0,0,0,,I have to remind myself what this function was.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.70,1:35:14.91,chinese,,0,0,0,,因为我现在要修改这个函数内容了，要知道这个函数内部是什么。
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.91,1:35:18.55,english,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to drag it higher up just so they're on the screen at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.91,1:35:18.55,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以我要把它拖到上面一点，让它们同时在屏幕上。
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.55,1:35:22.09,english,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go ahead now and temporarily move this over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.55,1:35:22.09,chinese,,0,0,0,,我现在要把它暂时移到这儿。
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.09,1:35:24.19,english,,0,0,0,,I'm going to temporarily detach this over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.09,1:35:24.19,chinese,,0,0,0,,再把这个暂时拆开。
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.19,1:35:24.70,english,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.70,1:35:33.76,english,,0,0,0,,Because what I thing I want to do is move my loop into the function itself, move the Play and the Wait into the loop.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.70,1:35:33.76,chinese,,0,0,0,,因为我想做的是将循环移到函数体里面，再把播放和等待移到循环里面。
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.76,1:35:35.47,english,,0,0,0,,But I don't want a hardcode 3.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.76,1:35:35.47,chinese,,0,0,0,,并且不想要硬编码 3 。
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.47,1:35:41.39,english,,0,0,0,,Notice that n here is its own oval I can drag a copy of n and just let it go there.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.47,1:35:41.39,chinese,,0,0,0,,注意，n 这个参数在椭圆形里面，我可以拖动 n 产生一个副本，让它去到需要的地方。
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.39,1:35:48.17,english,,0,0,0,,So now I have a new version of Meow that takes an argument, n, that tells Meow how many times to meow.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.39,1:35:48.17,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在，我有了一个新版本的 Meow，它接受一个参数 n，这个参数告诉 Meow 要喵喵叫多少次。
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.17,1:35:52.75,english,,0,0,0,,And now let me, again, drag this out of sight, out of mind, because who cares how I implemented it?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.17,1:35:52.75,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在，让我再一次把这个函数的细节抛到脑后，因为谁会在意我是如何实现的呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.75,1:35:54.88,english,,0,0,0,,Once it's implemented, it's sort of done.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.75,1:35:54.88,chinese,,0,0,0,,只要咱实现了这个函数，就等于完成了（可以无限制到处使用）。
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.88,1:35:58.07,english,,0,0,0,,Now my program is even better designed, in some sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.88,1:35:58.07,chinese,,0,0,0,,从某种意义上说，现在我的程序设计得更好了。
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.07,1:35:58.57,english,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.57,1:36:01.12,english,,0,0,0,,Because now it really just says what it means.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.57,1:36:01.12,chinese,,0,0,0,,因为现在，它真的是所见即所得了。
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.12,1:36:01.84,english,,0,0,0,,There's no loop.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.12,1:36:01.84,chinese,,0,0,0,,没有循环。
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.84,1:36:04.36,english,,0,0,0,,There's no repeat, no implementation details.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.84,1:36:04.36,chinese,,0,0,0,,没有重复，没有实施细节。
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.36,1:36:07.06,english,,0,0,0,,When Green Flag Clicked, Meow 3 Times.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.36,1:36:07.06,chinese,,0,0,0,,点击绿旗时，喵喵叫 3 次。
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.06,1:36:13.07,english,,0,0,0,,And so functions indeed let you implement algorithms, like they're just code that do something for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.06,1:36:13.07,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以说，函数的确可以帮助我们实现算法，\N它们说到底也只是一些组织好的、能执行任务的代码。
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.07,1:36:14.93,english,,0,0,0,,But they're also themselves abstractions.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.07,1:36:14.93,chinese,,0,0,0,,要知道函数本身也是抽象的。
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.93,1:36:15.43,english,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.43,1:36:17.66,english,,0,0,0,,Because once a function exists, it has a name.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.43,1:36:17.66,chinese,,0,0,0,,因为每创建一个函数，我们都会赋予它名字。
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.66,1:36:19.58,english,,0,0,0,,And you can think about it in that term.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.66,1:36:19.58,chinese,,0,0,0,,你可以从名字就知道这个函数的用途。
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.58,1:36:21.61,english,,0,0,0,,And you can use it by its name.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.58,1:36:21.61,chinese,,0,0,0,,你还可以根据它的名字来调用它。
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.61,1:36:27.73,english,,0,0,0,,You don't have to care or remember how the function itself was built, whether it's by you or even MIT.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.61,1:36:27.73,chinese,,0,0,0,,你不必关心记住函数本身是如何实现的，无论它是来自 MIT 还是你亲手打造的。
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.73,1:36:29.48,english,,0,0,0,,So again, here I'll click the Green Flag.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.73,1:36:29.48,chinese,,0,0,0,,再来一次，我要点一下绿旗。
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.48,1:36:30.31,english,,0,0,0,,It's the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.48,1:36:30.31,chinese,,0,0,0,,都是一样的。
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.31,1:36:32.29,english,,0,0,0,,[MEOWING]
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.13,1:36:38.25,english,,0,0,0,,So still correct, but better and better designed.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.13,1:36:38.25,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以还是正确的，但设计得更好、更完美。
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.25,1:36:42.27,english,,0,0,0,,And so any time, here and out, with Scratch, or soon C, and eventually Python
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.25,1:36:42.27,chinese,,0,0,0,,因此，无论何时何地，当你用 Scratch，或者很快就用到的 C，或者最终我们使用的 Python，
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.27,1:36:49.37,english,,0,0,0,,when you find yourself doing anything resembling Copy/Paste or again and again grabbing the same code, probably an opportunity to say, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.27,1:36:49.37,chinese,,0,0,0,,当你发现自己在做任何类似于复制/粘贴的事情，\N或者一次又一次地抓取相同的代码时，可能这就是一个时机说，停停。
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.37,1:36:59.58,english,,0,0,0,,Let me refactor this, so to speak, that is, rip out the code that seems to be repeated again and again and put it in its own function so you can give it a descriptive name and use and reuse it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.37,1:36:59.58,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们来重构一下吧！把那些看起来重复的代码删掉，把它放在自己的函数里面，\N这样你就可以给它一个描述性的名字，在任何地方重用它。
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.58,1:37:06.59,english,,0,0,0,,Any questions just yet on now saying or these loops or these functions that we're using?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.58,1:37:06.59,chinese,,0,0,0,,到现在为止说的这些循环或函数，大家还有什么问题想问吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.59,1:37:07.13,english,,0,0,0,,Yeah--
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.13,1:37:09.88,english,,0,0,0,,AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE]
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.88,1:37:12.30,english,,0,0,0,,DAVID J. MALAN: How did I make it so it meows three times?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.88,1:37:12.30,chinese,,0,0,0,,我是怎么让它喵喵叫三声的？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.30,1:37:15.06,english,,0,0,0,,So I originally only had a puzzle piece called Meow.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.30,1:37:15.06,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以，我最初只有一块拼图，叫做 Meow。
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.06,1:37:16.77,english,,0,0,0,,And I decided to improve it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.06,1:37:16.77,chinese,,0,0,0,,我决定改进它。
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.77,1:37:22.07,english,,0,0,0,,So I held down Control and I Right-clicked or Control-clicked on the pink puzzle piece at top left.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.77,1:37:22.07,chinese,,0,0,0,,于是，我用鼠标右键或 Ctrl 加左键，点击左上角的粉红色拼图。
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.07,1:37:23.12,english,,0,0,0,,And I clicked Edit.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.07,1:37:23.12,chinese,,0,0,0,,然后我点击了 "编辑"。
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.12,1:37:28.79,english,,0,0,0,,And that brought back the original interface that lets me add some arguments to the puzzle piece itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.12,1:37:28.79,chinese,,0,0,0,,这让我又回到了开始的界面，可以为新拼图添加一些参数。
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.79,1:37:31.25,english,,0,0,0,,And I clicked Add an Input on the left here.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.79,1:37:31.25,chinese,,0,0,0,,然后我点击左侧的 "添加输入"。
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.25,1:37:34.26,english,,0,0,0,,And then I clicked on Add a Label over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.25,1:37:34.26,chinese,,0,0,0,,然后点击这里的添加标签。
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.26,1:37:36.96,english,,0,0,0,,So that just lets you customize it even further.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.26,1:37:36.96,chinese,,0,0,0,,这样就可以进一步定制它了。
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.96,1:37:38.49,english,,0,0,0,,All right, so we've done this.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.96,1:37:38.49,chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧，我们已经完成了。
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.49,1:37:41.90,english,,0,0,0,,Let's add one of those other primitives too to do something optionally.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.49,1:37:41.90,chinese,,0,0,0,,让我们再添加一个基础函数，来做点别的事情。
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.90,1:37:50.54,english,,0,0,0,,So how about we make the cat meow only if it's being petted by a human, as by moving the mouse to hover over the cat, like a human would pet a cat?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.90,1:37:50.54,chinese,,0,0,0,,比如，猫咪只在人类抚摸时才叫，\N那我们移动鼠标悬停在猫咪上方时让它喵喵叫，怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.54,1:37:55.11,english,,0,0,0,,Well, let me go ahead and throw away the meowing for now.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.54,1:37:55.11,chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧，让我先把 Meow 扔掉吧。
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.11,1:37:57.08,english,,0,0,0,,And let me simplify it by just using a sound.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.11,1:37:57.08,chinese,,0,0,0,,猫叫的这个过程就用一声喵来简化。
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.08,1:37:58.50,english,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go ahead and do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.08,1:37:58.50,chinese,,0,0,0,,我要这样...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.50,1:38:08.93,english,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go ahead and have a Control block that says If, because I want to implement the idea of if the cursor is touching the cat, then play sound meow.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.50,1:38:08.93,chinese,,0,0,0,,我还得用 if 条件语句，因为想实现 "如果光标碰到猫，就播放喵喵声" 的想法。
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.93,1:38:10.71,english,,0,0,0,,Or I could use my same pink puzzle piece.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.93,1:38:10.71,chinese,,0,0,0,,或者，我也可以用刚才自己那块粉色拼图。
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.71,1:38:14.15,english,,0,0,0,,But I'm going to throw that away and focus only now on the sounds.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.71,1:38:14.15,chinese,,0,0,0,,但我现在要抛开这些，只关注声音。
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.15,1:38:15.84,english,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.15,1:38:15.84,chinese,,0,0,0,,我要这么做
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.84,1:38:19.59,english,,0,0,0,,If touching mouse pointer-- so I need to sense something about the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.84,1:38:19.59,chinese,,0,0,0,,如果触摸鼠标指针—— 这应该在 Sensing 感知模块下面。
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.59,1:38:22.50,english,,0,0,0,,And we saw this earlier-- so If Touching Mouse Pointer.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.59,1:38:22.50,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们在前面已经看到过了，所以组合 "if" 和 "触摸鼠标指针"。
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.50,1:38:24.81,english,,0,0,0,,So notice this shape here, way too big.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.50,1:38:24.81,chinese,,0,0,0,,注意这个形状，有点大。
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.81,1:38:25.92,english,,0,0,0,,But it is the right shape.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.81,1:38:25.92,chinese,,0,0,0,,但它的形状是合适的。
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.92,1:38:29.21,english,,0,0,0,,So if I hover just right, it'll snap into place.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.92,1:38:29.21,chinese,,0,0,0,,因此，如果我放的位置恰到好处，它会适配进去。
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.21,1:38:34.85,english,,0,0,0,,And this now, in blue, is my Boolean expression, a yes/no question, true false.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.21,1:38:34.85,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在这个蓝色块是一个布尔表达式，也就是一个是/否、真/假的问题。
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.85,1:38:36.86,english,,0,0,0,,"If" is a conditional.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.85,1:38:36.86,chinese,,0,0,0,,"if" 是一个条件。
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.86,1:38:38.10,english,,0,0,0,,And what do I want to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.86,1:38:38.10,chinese,,0,0,0,,我想做什么来着？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.10,1:38:42.29,english,,0,0,0,,Well, if the cat is touching the mouse pointer,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.10,1:38:42.29,chinese,,0,0,0,,嗯，如果鼠标指针碰到猫的话，
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.29,1:38:44.97,english,,0,0,0,,I want to go ahead and play sound meow until done.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.29,1:38:44.97,chinese,,0,0,0,,我想播放声音喵到完成。
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.97,1:38:46.08,english,,0,0,0,,So let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.97,1:38:46.08,chinese,,0,0,0,,那就这么办吧。
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.08,1:38:48.80,english,,0,0,0,,I'm going to hit Green Flag, click.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.08,1:38:48.80,chinese,,0,0,0,,我要点一下绿旗。
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.80,1:38:51.35,english,,0,0,0,,Now nothing's happened yet because it's a conditional, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.80,1:38:51.35,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在什么都还没发生，因为这是一个条件判断，是吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.35,1:38:53.80,english,,0,0,0,,It's only supposed to do something if I'm touching the cat.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.35,1:38:53.80,chinese,,0,0,0,,只有在我摸猫的时候，它才会有所反应。
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.80,1:38:55.55,english,,0,0,0,,Let me move the cursor over to the cat.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.80,1:38:55.55,chinese,,0,0,0,,让我把光标移到猫身上。
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.55,1:38:59.36,english,,0,0,0,,And-- wait for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.55,1:38:59.36,chinese,,0,0,0,,等一等，
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.36,1:39:02.33,english,,0,0,0,,Hmm-- another bug.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.36,1:39:02.33,chinese,,0,0,0,,嗯，出 bug 了。
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.33,1:39:09.02,english,,0,0,0,,Why is the cat not meowing even though I very explicitly said, If Touching Mouse Pointer, Meow?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.33,1:39:09.02,chinese,,0,0,0,,为什么我明明设置了 "如果触摸鼠标指针，就喵喵叫" ，猫却不喵喵叫呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.02,1:39:10.29,english,,0,0,0,,Yeah, in the middle--
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.02,1:39:10.29,chinese,,0,0,0,,中间这位请讲。
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.29,1:39:11.89,english,,0,0,0,,AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE]
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.89,1:39:15.44,english,,0,0,0,,DAVID J. MALAN: Yeah, this is-- again, my computer's just so darn fast, like yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.89,1:39:15.44,chinese,,0,0,0,,对的，我们的电脑都快得要命。
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.44,1:39:18.65,english,,0,0,0,,I click the Green Flag, it asks the question, am I touching the mouse pointer?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.44,1:39:18.65,chinese,,0,0,0,,我点击绿旗的时候，它会问，这个时候的鼠标指针是否和猫有接触？
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.65,1:39:21.35,english,,0,0,0,,Well, no, because my cursor was up there, not touching the cat.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.65,1:39:21.35,chinese,,0,0,0,,嗯，没有，因为我的光标在绿旗的位置，没碰到猫。
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.35,1:39:22.37,english,,0,0,0,,It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.35,1:39:22.37,chinese,,0,0,0,,这太迟了！
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.37,1:39:23.57,english,,0,0,0,,The cat's out of the bag.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.37,1:39:23.57,chinese,,0,0,0,,猫已经出来了，程序结束了。
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.57,1:39:28.49,english,,0,0,0,,And so we have to instead solve this by some other means.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.57,1:39:28.49,chinese,,0,0,0,,因此，我们必须用其他方法来解决这个问题。
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.49,1:39:29.94,english,,0,0,0,,How can we fix this?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.49,1:39:29.94,chinese,,0,0,0,,怎么解决这个问题？
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.94,1:39:31.47,english,,0,0,0,,How do we fix that sort of race?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.94,1:39:31.47,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们该怎么解决这种竞速比赛？
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.47,1:39:31.97,english,,0,0,0,,Yeah--
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.97,1:39:32.69,english,,0,0,0,,AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE]
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.69,1:39:38.57,english,,0,0,0,,DAVID J. MALAN: Yeah, so why don't we just keep asking the question until I eventually am or am not actually petting the cat?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.69,1:39:38.57,chinese,,0,0,0,,是啊，那我们为什么不一直问这个问题，直到我最终真的触摸到猫猫呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.57,1:39:40.61,english,,0,0,0,,So let me detach this temporarily.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.57,1:39:40.61,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以，我们暂时放下这个问题。
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.61,1:39:42.05,english,,0,0,0,,Let me go under Control.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.61,1:39:42.05,chinese,,0,0,0,,来到 Control 模块下。
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.05,1:39:46.14,english,,0,0,0,,Let me go under-- instead of repeat some finite number of times, let's just do it forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.05,1:39:46.14,chinese,,0,0,0,,到这个类别下看看—— 与其重复个几次，不如让它一直检测是否在摸猫猫。
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.14,1:39:49.07,english,,0,0,0,,So sometimes loops that do work forever are a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.14,1:39:49.07,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以有时候，一直循环也是件好事。
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.07,1:39:54.72,english,,0,0,0,,The clock on your phone, that's in a loop forever because you want it to always tell time and not stop at the end of the day.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.07,1:39:54.72,chinese,,0,0,0,,你手机上的时钟就是永远在循环，因为你希望它永远显示正确时间，而不是在一天结束时停止。
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.72,1:39:58.91,english,,0,0,0,,So sometimes you do want code to loop forever, as in this case.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.72,1:39:58.91,chinese,,0,0,0,,因此，有时你确实希望代码永远循环下去，就像这个例子一样。
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.91,1:40:00.83,english,,0,0,0,,So let me go ahead and drag and drop it there.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.91,1:40:00.83,chinese,,0,0,0,,我来把它拖到这儿。
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.83,1:40:02.75,english,,0,0,0,,Let me, again, click the Green Flag.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.83,1:40:02.75,chinese,,0,0,0,,让我再点下绿旗。
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.75,1:40:03.90,english,,0,0,0,,Nothing's happening yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.75,1:40:03.90,chinese,,0,0,0,,什么都没发生。
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.90,1:40:06.30,english,,0,0,0,,But notice, the program is still running.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.90,1:40:06.30,chinese,,0,0,0,,但请注意，程序仍在运行。
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.30,1:40:10.70,english,,0,0,0,,And so if I move my cursor, move my cursor, move my cursor, and--
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.30,1:40:10.70,chinese,,0,0,0,,因此，如果我移动光标，移动光标，移动光标，然后——
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.70,1:40:12.88,english,,0,0,0,,[MEOWING]
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.88,1:40:14.55,english,,0,0,0,,OK, so maybe we could add some Waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.88,1:40:14.55,chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧，也许我们可以增加一些停顿。
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.55,1:40:17.75,english,,0,0,0,,But the cat does not want to be pet, in this case.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.55,1:40:17.75,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在这种情况，猫听上去并不想被摸摸（因为没有停顿，在循环叫）。
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.75,1:40:20.22,english,,0,0,0,,But it's indeed conditional.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.75,1:40:20.22,chinese,,0,0,0,,但这确实是个条件判断。
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.22,1:40:24.29,english,,0,0,0,,So there we have an incarnation in Scratch of doing something conditionally.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.22,1:40:24.29,chinese,,0,0,0,,因此，我们在 Scratch 中看到了 "在条件下做某事"。
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.29,1:40:26.79,english,,0,0,0,,Now, we can make this really cool, really fast, if you will.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.29,1:40:26.79,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在，我们可以让它变得超级酷。
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.79,1:40:28.44,english,,0,0,0,,Let me stop this version.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.79,1:40:28.44,chinese,,0,0,0,,我先停止现在这个永久循环。
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.44,1:40:31.27,english,,0,0,0,,Let me go ahead and do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.44,1:40:31.27,chinese,,0,0,0,,接着是这样。
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.27,1:40:33.27,english,,0,0,0,,Let me go ahead and throw all of this away.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.27,1:40:33.27,chinese,,0,0,0,,把这些都扔掉吧。
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.27,1:40:36.21,english,,0,0,0,,Let me go into my little Extensions bucket over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.27,1:40:36.21,chinese,,0,0,0,,进入这个扩展插件集。
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.21,1:40:40.62,english,,0,0,0,,And let me do Video Sensing, since most laptops or phones these days have cameras.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.21,1:40:40.62,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们想要视频感应，因为现在大多数笔记本电脑或手机都有摄像头。
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.62,1:40:44.19,english,,0,0,0,,And there, indeed, I am, with Sanders behind me.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.62,1:40:44.19,chinese,,0,0,0,,我确实出现在了屏幕里面。
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.19,1:40:45.78,english,,0,0,0,,And let me do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.19,1:40:45.78,chinese,,0,0,0,,接着来吧。
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.78,1:40:48.90,english,,0,0,0,,When Video Motion-- and let me get out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.78,1:40:48.90,chinese,,0,0,0,,当视频动态... 我先离开摄像头。
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.90,1:40:51.82,english,,0,0,0,,When Video Motion is Greater Than some value.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.90,1:40:51.82,chinese,,0,0,0,,当视频动态大于某个值时。
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.82,1:40:56.67,english,,0,0,0,,So 10 is the default. This is just a number that measures how much motion there is or isn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.82,1:40:56.67,chinese,,0,0,0,,10 是默认值，这只是一个衡量动作幅度大小的数字。
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.67,1:40:58.29,english,,0,0,0,,So small number is like no motion.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.67,1:40:58.29,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以，数字小就是说没怎么动。
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.29,1:40:59.92,english,,0,0,0,,Big number is lots of motion.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.29,1:40:59.92,chinese,,0,0,0,,数字大就是大幅度的动作。
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.92,1:41:03.12,english,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to choose 50, somewhat arbitrarily here-- so 50.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.92,1:41:03.12,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以我选择 50，有点随意，就 50 吧。
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.12,1:41:05.37,english,,0,0,0,,This is not normal to program off to the side.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.12,1:41:05.37,chinese,,0,0,0,,站在电脑一旁编程，多少有点不正常。
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.37,1:41:08.13,english,,0,0,0,,But I'm now going to say this.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.37,1:41:08.13,chinese,,0,0,0,,我现在要说的是，
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.13,1:41:14.46,english,,0,0,0,,When Video Motion is 50, go ahead and Play Sound Meow like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.13,1:41:14.46,chinese,,0,0,0,,当 "Video Motion" 为 50 时，像这样播放一声喵。
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.46,1:41:16.17,english,,0,0,0,,So the cat is still in that world.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.46,1:41:16.17,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以，这只猫还在那个世界里。
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.17,1:41:18.97,english,,0,0,0,,I'm going to stop the program and rerun it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.17,1:41:18.97,chinese,,0,0,0,,我要停止程序再重新运行。
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.97,1:41:21.09,english,,0,0,0,,So here we go, Green Flag.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.97,1:41:21.09,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们开始吧，点绿旗。
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.09,1:41:30.64,english,,0,0,0,,And now here comes-- all right, this is a little creepy, the way I'm petting the cat, but-- and-- [SIGH]
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.09,1:41:30.64,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在要来了—— 好吧，这有点吓人，这种抚摸猫的方式，但是...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.60,1:41:32.94,english,,0,0,0,,[MEOWING]
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.94,1:41:33.44,english,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.44,1:41:35.75,english,,0,0,0,,[LAUGHTER]
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.75,1:41:36.29,english,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.75,1:41:36.29,chinese,,0,0,0,,好了。
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.29,1:41:37.91,english,,0,0,0,,OK, so 50 was too big of a number.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.29,1:41:37.91,chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧，50 这个数字太大了。
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.91,1:41:39.50,english,,0,0,0,,I have to pet the cat faster.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.91,1:41:39.50,chinese,,0,0,0,,我得特别快地摸猫咪。
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.50,1:41:41.92,english,,0,0,0,,[MEOWING]
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.90,1:41:44.94,english,,0,0,0,,Whereas this, if--
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.90,1:41:44.94,chinese,,0,0,0,,那这样，如果慢点呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.94,1:41:46.41,english,,0,0,0,,I don't know--
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.94,1:41:46.41,chinese,,0,0,0,,我不知道。
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.41,1:41:48.33,english,,0,0,0,,[LAUGHTER]
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.33,1:41:49.92,english,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so--
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.92,1:41:50.71,english,,0,0,0,,[MEOW]
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.71,1:41:55.41,english,,0,0,0,,OK, so you can make things even more interactive in this way by just assembling different puzzle pieces.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.71,1:41:55.41,chinese,,0,0,0,,好了，只要把不同的拼图拼在一起，就能让很多东西参与互动。
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.41,1:41:58.05,english,,0,0,0,,And honestly, there are so many different puzzle pieces in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.41,1:41:58.05,chinese,,0,0,0,,其实吧，这里有很多不同的拼图。
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.05,1:42:00.61,english,,0,0,0,,We're not going to even scratch the surface of a lot of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.05,1:42:00.61,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们只是浅尝辄止，不会对其中的很多内容细细研究。
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.61,1:42:02.94,english,,0,0,0,,But they generally just do what they say.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.61,1:42:02.94,chinese,,0,0,0,,但他们一般都是所见（函数名）即所得（函数效果）。
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.94,1:42:12.97,english,,0,0,0,,And indeed, when you see on the screen here this pallet of puzzle pieces, really a lot of programming, especially early on, when learning a language, is just trying different things and try and fail.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.94,1:42:12.97,chinese,,0,0,0,,实际上，当你在屏幕上看到这些个拼图块，处于学习一门语言的早期阶段时，\N编程就是尝试不同的方法，不断试错和改进。
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.97,1:42:20.00,english,,0,0,0,,And if it doesn't work quite right, look for an alternative solution there too, as even I just had to do a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.97,1:42:20.00,chinese,,0,0,0,,如果效果不如预期，也可以寻找其他解决方案，就像我刚才不得不做的那样。
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.00,1:42:24.72,english,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go ahead and use, actually, how about another example of something a predecessor of yours made?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.00,1:42:24.72,chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧，让我们继续，用你们前辈做的另一个例子怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.72,1:42:28.83,english,,0,0,0,,Let me go ahead and grab a program I opened in advance here called
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.72,1:42:28.83,chinese,,0,0,0,,让我打开一个提前准备好的程序，叫做"打地鼠"。
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.83,1:42:38.89,english,,0,0,0,,Whack-A-Mole Might we get a brave volunteer to come up, who is willing to whack a mole with their head, virtually?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.83,1:42:38.89,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们能不能请一位勇敢的志愿者上来，用头模拟着打鼹鼠？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.89,1:42:40.77,english,,0,0,0,,Maybe-- OK, let's see, how about in way back?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.89,1:42:40.77,chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧，我想想，后面这位怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.77,1:42:42.30,english,,0,0,0,,You want to come on down?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.77,1:42:42.30,chinese,,0,0,0,,你想下来吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.30,1:42:45.32,english,,0,0,0,,All right, come on down.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.30,1:42:45.32,chinese,,0,0,0,,好了，来吧。
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.32,1:42:47.16,english,,0,0,0,,Sure, a round of applause for our volunteer.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.32,1:42:47.16,chinese,,0,0,0,,当然，掌声送给我们的志愿者。
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.16,1:42:49.38,english,,0,0,0,,[APPLAUSE]
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.13,1:43:01.17,english,,0,0,0,,All right, so here we have-- come on down.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.13,1:43:01.17,chinese,,0,0,0,,好了，来吧。
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.17,1:43:01.97,english,,0,0,0,,AUDIENCE: Hi there.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.97,1:43:02.72,english,,0,0,0,,DAVID J. MALAN: What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.97,1:43:02.72,chinese,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.72,1:43:03.32,english,,0,0,0,,AUDIENCE: I'm Josh.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.32,1:43:05.69,english,,0,0,0,,DAVID J. MALAN: Oh, actually, say it into the microphone.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.32,1:43:05.69,chinese,,0,0,0,,对着麦克风说吧。
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.69,1:43:06.95,english,,0,0,0,,AUDIENCE: Hi, I'm Josh.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.95,1:43:07.67,english,,0,0,0,,DAVID J. MALAN: OK, nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.67,1:43:08.24,english,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Josh.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.67,1:43:08.24,chinese,,0,0,0,,欢迎， Josh 。
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.24,1:43:08.78,english,,0,0,0,,Come on over.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.24,1:43:08.78,chinese,,0,0,0,,过来吧。
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.78,1:43:10.85,english,,0,0,0,,[APPLAUSE]
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.85,1:43:12.89,english,,0,0,0,,All right, so same idea here--
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.85,1:43:12.89,chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧，也是一样的。
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.89,1:43:13.85,english,,0,0,0,,I'll take the mic back.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.89,1:43:13.85,chinese,,0,0,0,,我把麦克风拿着。
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.85,1:43:15.23,english,,0,0,0,,You'll have to stand in front of the camera.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.85,1:43:15.23,chinese,,0,0,0,,你得站在摄像头前面。
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.23,1:43:20.15,english,,0,0,0,,In just a moment, you're going to have to position your head in a box that your classmate from yesteryear created.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.23,1:43:20.15,chinese,,0,0,0,,一会儿，你把头放到屏幕中间的框里。
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.15,1:43:22.34,english,,0,0,0,,[MUSIC PLAYING]
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.84,1:43:24.49,english,,0,0,0,,And we'll start with Beginner.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.84,1:43:24.49,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们从初级难度开始。
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.49,1:43:25.18,english,,0,0,0,,AUDIENCE: OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.18,1:43:28.16,english,,0,0,0,,DAVID J. MALAN: So line your head up in the box in a moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.18,1:43:28.16,chinese,,0,0,0,,请把你的头放在框里。
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.16,1:43:29.14,english,,0,0,0,,AUDIENCE: All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.43,1:43:39.87,english,,0,0,0,,[LAUGHTER]
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.80,1:43:45.39,english,,0,0,0,,DAVID J. MALAN: Nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.39,1:43:46.15,english,,0,0,0,,12 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.39,1:43:46.15,chinese,,0,0,0,,还有 12 秒。
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.50,1:43:53.79,english,,0,0,0,,5 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.79,1:43:55.71,english,,0,0,0,,Notice the score's up to 18 already.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.79,1:43:55.71,chinese,,0,0,0,,注意分数已经到 18 分了。
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.71,1:43:58.41,english,,0,0,0,,Pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.71,1:43:58.41,chinese,,0,0,0,,相当不错。
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.41,1:44:00.99,english,,0,0,0,,All right, a round of applause for Josh, if we could.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.41,1:44:00.99,chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧，如果可以的话，请为 Josh 鼓掌。
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.99,1:44:03.44,english,,0,0,0,,[APPLAUSE]
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.38,1:44:11.33,english,,0,0,0,,So notice how using some fairly simple primitives, things do get interesting pretty fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.38,1:44:11.33,chinese,,0,0,0,,请注意，使用一些相当简单的基元，我们很快就能做出有意思的软件。
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.33,1:44:12.56,english,,0,0,0,,And how was that implemented?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.33,1:44:12.56,chinese,,0,0,0,,那是怎么做到的呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.56,1:44:14.56,english,,0,0,0,,Well, there were probably at least four sprites.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.56,1:44:14.56,chinese,,0,0,0,,嗯，至少得有四个精灵。
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.56,1:44:16.22,english,,0,0,0,,So you're not confined to just one cat.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.56,1:44:16.22,chinese,,0,0,0,,你不能只局限于一只猫。
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.22,1:44:18.93,english,,0,0,0,,You can create more and more sprites, change what they look like.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.22,1:44:18.93,chinese,,0,0,0,,你可以创建越来越多的精灵，改变它们的模样。
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.93,1:44:20.93,english,,0,0,0,,So they actually look like a mole, in this case.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.93,1:44:20.93,chinese,,0,0,0,,在刚才那个例子里面就是鼹鼠。
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.93,1:44:23.99,english,,0,0,0,,There's probably some conditionals in there, some loops for 30 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.93,1:44:23.99,chinese,,0,0,0,,其中可能包含一些条件判断，一些持续 30 秒的循环。
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.99,1:44:31.55,english,,0,0,0,,That's checking if Josh's head's movement is exceeding some value over this way or over this way, then increment something called a variable.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.99,1:44:31.55,chinese,,0,0,0,,这就是检查 Josh 的头部移动速度是否超过了某个值，\N然后递增一个叫做变量（Variable）的东西。
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.55,1:44:32.45,english,,0,0,0,,We'll see those too.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.55,1:44:32.45,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们也会看到的。
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.45,1:44:42.35,english,,0,0,0,,Just like in algebra you might have x and y and z, storing values like numbers, so can computer programs, have variables called x or y or z, or more descriptively called Score,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.45,1:44:42.35,chinese,,0,0,0,,就像代数中的 x、y 和 z，可以像数字一样存储数值，\N计算机程序也可以有名为 x 或 y 或 z 的变量，在这个例子里，就是 Score，
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.35,1:44:49.63,english,,0,0,0,,as in this case at top right, or another variable called Countdown, typically one word in code, but in this case two words, that just store some value.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.35,1:44:49.63,chinese,,0,0,0,,或另一个名为 Countdown 的变量，在代码中变量通常是一个单词，\N但在本例中是两个单词，它们都是拿来存储一些数值。
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.35,1:44:49.63,annotation,,0,0,0,,*注：多少个单词其实无所谓，但是不能用空格分开，这里的 Countdown 就是连写的。
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.63,1:44:54.60,english,,0,0,0,,So there's probably some math going on in there whereby the author of this program just is incrementing
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.63,1:44:54.60,chinese,,0,0,0,,因此，这里可能有一些数学运算，程序的编写者只是在递增这个变量，
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.60,1:45:00.57,english,,0,0,0,,that is, adding 1 and 1 every time it detected that a mole had been whacked, in this case, with movement.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.60,1:45:00.57,chinese,,0,0,0,,也就是说，每次检测到鼹鼠被"捶打"（在这里是"移动"）时，就会一个一个地递增。
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.57,1:45:07.56,english,,0,0,0,,So back in the day, I, myself, actually implemented my very first program in Scratch when I was a graduate student, actually, at MIT
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.57,1:45:07.56,chinese,,0,0,0,,想当时我读研究生时，就用 Scratch 实现了我的第一个程序。
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.56,1:45:15.50,english,,0,0,0,,cross-registered at MIT, taking a class from MIT's Media Lab, specifically, the lifelong kindergarten group, which is the group that created Scratch, itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.56,1:45:15.50,chinese,,0,0,0,,当时我在麻省理工学院注册交叉参加了一门\N Media Lab lifelong kindergarten 小组的课程，这个小组其实就是 Scratch 的创造者。
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.50,1:45:27.12,english,,0,0,0,,And the program I wrote all those years ago and still rather cling to is a little something here called Oscartime, that I thought I'd play just a quick excerpt of myself here.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.50,1:45:27.12,chinese,,0,0,0,,我多年前编写的，至今仍念念不忘的程序是一个叫做 "奥斯卡时间" 的小玩意儿，\N我想在这里为自己播放一段简短的片段。
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.12,1:45:38.06,english,,0,0,0,,So in this case, consider, as the music starts playing, how this program, which is much more sophisticated, certainly, than the earliest "Say hello" examples we just did might also be implemented.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.12,1:45:38.06,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在当音乐开始播放时，请想一想这个程序是如何实现的，\N当然，这个程序要比我们刚才最早做的 "Say hello" 例子要复杂得多。
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.06,1:45:40.74,english,,0,0,0,,Let me go ahead now and click the Green Flag.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.06,1:45:40.74,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在让我点击绿旗。
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.74,1:45:44.95,english,,0,0,0,,[MUSIC - OSCAR THE GROUCH, "I LOVE TRASH"]
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.95,1:45:46.97,english,,0,0,0,,OSCAR THE GROUCH: (SINGING) Oh, I love trash.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.97,1:45:51.97,english,,0,0,0,,DAVID J. MALAN: OK, so some trash is moving, presumably in some kind of loop from the top.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.97,1:45:51.97,chinese,,0,0,0,,好的，一些垃圾在动，大概是从顶部开始借助循环移动的。
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.97,1:45:56.44,english,,0,0,0,,If I'm touching the mouse cursor, it follows me.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.97,1:45:56.44,chinese,,0,0,0,,如果用光标碰到，它就会自动跟随。
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.44,1:45:59.92,english,,0,0,0,,If I hover over the trash can, it responds.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.44,1:45:59.92,chinese,,0,0,0,,如果我把鼠标悬停在垃圾桶上，它就会有所反应。
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.92,1:46:06.91,english,,0,0,0,,If I let go, in some kind of loop, Oscar pops out, creates a variable with the current score.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.92,1:46:06.91,chinese,,0,0,0,,如果我松开手，Oscar 就会跳出来，这里其实有一个当前分数的变量。
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.91,1:46:07.90,english,,0,0,0,,And it happens again.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.91,1:46:07.90,chinese,,0,0,0,,再来看一次。
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.90,1:46:09.98,english,,0,0,0,,OSCAR THE GROUCH: (SINGING) It's awful, the holes.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.98,1:46:11.95,english,,0,0,0,,And the laces are torn.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.95,1:46:16.03,english,,0,0,0,,A gift from my mother the day I was born.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.03,1:46:20.05,english,,0,0,0,,I love it because it's trash.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.05,1:46:21.07,english,,0,0,0,,Oh, I--
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.07,1:46:24.05,english,,0,0,0,,DAVID J. MALAN: It's pretty easy at first but--
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.07,1:46:24.05,chinese,,0,0,0,,一开始很容易，但是——
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.05,1:46:26.41,english,,0,0,0,,OSCAR THE GROUCH: (SINGING) --anything dirty or dingy--
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.41,1:46:30.23,english,,0,0,0,,DAVID J. MALAN: So I don't need to keep playing this up on stage in front of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.41,1:46:30.23,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以我不需要一直在讲台上当着所有人的面玩这个。
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.23,1:46:32.95,english,,0,0,0,,So my score is already now up to some 6 or so.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.23,1:46:32.95,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在我差不多拿了 6 分。
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.95,1:46:35.90,english,,0,0,0,,But in a moment, too, you'll see that it's going to escalate.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.95,1:46:35.90,chinese,,0,0,0,,过一会你就能看到，游戏升级了。
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.90,1:46:38.08,english,,0,0,0,,So I'm taking into account some time apparently.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.90,1:46:38.08,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以我显然考虑到了时间问题。
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.08,1:46:38.98,english,,0,0,0,,So now--
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.98,1:46:42.34,english,,0,0,0,,OSCAR THE GROUCH: (SINGING) I have here some newspaper, 13 months old.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.34,1:46:45.01,english,,0,0,0,,DAVID J. MALAN: So more and more sprites are suddenly appearing.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.34,1:46:45.01,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以越来越多的精灵突然出现了。
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.01,1:46:48.04,english,,0,0,0,,And notice, that each time they're appearing from a different part of the screen.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.01,1:46:48.04,chinese,,0,0,0,,注意，每次它们都是从屏幕的不同地方出现的。
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.04,1:46:52.27,english,,0,0,0,,That's an illusion, perhaps, too, that-- pick a random number between x and y.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.04,1:46:52.27,chinese,,0,0,0,,这也许也是一种幻觉—— 真实情况是在 x 和 y 之间随便选一个数字。
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.27,1:46:56.03,english,,0,0,0,,So you can actually pick some range of values to have the game constantly changing.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.27,1:46:56.03,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们实际上可以选择一些数值范围，让游戏产生无数的变化。
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.03,1:47:00.86,english,,0,0,0,,And indeed, I'm going to go ahead and click Stop, since I spent like eight hours plus, years ago, making this.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.03,1:47:00.86,chinese,,0,0,0,,那现在演示得停一停了，好多年前我花了差不多八个多小时来制作这个。
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.86,1:47:04.81,english,,0,0,0,,And I can never listen to the song again, not that I should be anyway at this point in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.86,1:47:04.81,chinese,,0,0,0,,这首歌真听不了一点，反正我现在上课也不应该听。
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.81,1:47:09.67,english,,0,0,0,,But this song is synchronized then with a lot of the actions that's happening.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.81,1:47:09.67,chinese,,0,0,0,,其实在这个程序里，一边在播放这首歌，一边还有其他操作在同步执行。
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.67,1:47:12.13,english,,0,0,0,,And ultimately, there's just a lot of building blocks.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.67,1:47:12.13,chinese,,0,0,0,,归根结底，这都是一些拼图块。
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.13,1:47:15.61,english,,0,0,0,,But I didn't sit down and implement Oscartime, as I called it, all at once.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.13,1:47:15.61,chinese,,0,0,0,,我那时候没什么头绪，不是坐下来就把 "Oscartime" 编写完成的。
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.61,1:47:17.50,english,,0,0,0,,I really did take baby steps, so to speak.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.61,1:47:17.50,chinese,,0,0,0,,可以说，我真的是坐着宝宝巴士过来的。
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.50,1:47:24.22,english,,0,0,0,,And I figured out, well, how could I decompose this vision I had at the time to create this game ultimately?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.50,1:47:24.22,chinese,,0,0,0,,然后我就想，好吧，我该如何分解我当时的愿景，最终创造出这款游戏呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.22,1:47:26.47,english,,0,0,0,,And how do I bite off maybe the easiest parts first?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.22,1:47:26.47,chinese,,0,0,0,,我该如何先蚕食最容易的一部分？
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.47,1:47:31.12,english,,0,0,0,,And honestly, the first thing I did was I found this image, and I just dragged and dropped it into Scratch--
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.47,1:47:31.12,chinese,,0,0,0,,老实说，我做的第一件事，就是找到了这张图片，然后把它拖进了 Scratch——
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.12,1:47:33.58,english,,0,0,0,,OK, done-- like, lamppost is installed.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.12,1:47:33.58,chinese,,0,0,0,,好了，搞定—— 灯柱安装完毕。
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.58,1:47:34.57,english,,0,0,0,,It doesn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.58,1:47:34.57,chinese,,0,0,0,,它啥也做不了。
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.57,1:47:35.45,english,,0,0,0,,It's not interactive.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.57,1:47:35.45,chinese,,0,0,0,,这不是可以交互的。
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.45,1:47:37.99,english,,0,0,0,,But I at least set the stage, so to speak, for the program.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.45,1:47:37.99,chinese,,0,0,0,,但我至少为这个程序做了铺垫。
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.99,1:47:39.37,english,,0,0,0,,Then what else might I have done?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.99,1:47:39.37,chinese,,0,0,0,,那我还能做点什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.37,1:47:40.64,english,,0,0,0,,Well, let me do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.37,1:47:40.64,chinese,,0,0,0,,来看看吧。
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.64,1:47:48.98,english,,0,0,0,,Let me go ahead and open up in another editor here an early incarnation of Oscartime by doing this.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.64,1:47:48.98,chinese,,0,0,0,,我现在要在另一个编辑器中打开 Oscartime 的早期版本。
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.98,1:47:51.22,english,,0,0,0,,Let me go into Oscartime here.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.98,1:47:51.22,chinese,,0,0,0,,让我打开奥斯卡时间。
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.22,1:47:52.51,english,,0,0,0,,Let me full screen this.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.22,1:47:52.51,chinese,,0,0,0,,全屏显示。
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.51,1:47:59.68,english,,0,0,0,,And here you have-- let me hide the trash for just a moment-- is what I might call the second version of my program
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.51,1:47:59.68,chinese,,0,0,0,,这就是，让我先把垃圾藏起来，Oscartime 的第二个版本
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.68,1:48:06.26,english,,0,0,0,,wherein, at the top right of the stage here, I had the lamppost, which I just dragged and dropped and got going, but then I added an actual sprite.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.68,1:48:06.26,chinese,,0,0,0,,其中，在舞台的左上方有一个灯柱，我只是拖放过来就行了，\N但随后我又添加了一个实际的精灵（垃圾桶）。
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.26,1:48:09.10,english,,0,0,0,,And it has to be a sprite if you want it to do things interactively.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.26,1:48:09.10,chinese,,0,0,0,,如果你想让它进行交互式操作，它就必须是一个精灵。
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.10,1:48:10.42,english,,0,0,0,,The lamppost-- not a sprite.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.10,1:48:10.42,chinese,,0,0,0,,这灯柱不是精灵。
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.42,1:48:14.68,english,,0,0,0,,It's just an image a costume, if you will, for the whole stage itself, a backdrop.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.42,1:48:14.68,chinese,,0,0,0,,这只是整个 Stage 本身的一个形象，一套服装，一个背景。
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.68,1:48:20.24,english,,0,0,0,,But this thing is indeed a sprite because it needs to respond to code and events, like dragging and dropping.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.68,1:48:20.24,chinese,,0,0,0,,但这个垃圾桶确实是一个精灵，因为它需要对代码和事件（如拖放）做出响应。
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.24,1:48:23.96,english,,0,0,0,,So what might I have done early on with that code?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.24,1:48:23.96,chinese,,0,0,0,,那么，我早期可能会用代码做些什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.96,1:48:32.17,english,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe the first version would have been something like this, whereby my very first version of Oscartime might have said something like, oh, this.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.96,1:48:32.17,chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧，也许第一个版本会是这样的。
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.17,1:48:35.50,english,,0,0,0,,How about, let me control the program as before-- or, rather, events.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.17,1:48:35.50,chinese,,0,0,0,,差不多，让我像刚才一样控制程序，或者说，控制事件。
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.50,1:48:38.63,english,,0,0,0,,When the Green Flag is clicked, what do I want to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.50,1:48:38.63,chinese,,0,0,0,,点击绿旗后，我想做什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.63,1:48:43.60,english,,0,0,0,,Well, I want to go ahead and forever do something like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.63,1:48:43.60,chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧，我首先想要一个 forever 的循环。
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.60,1:48:46.68,english,,0,0,0,,Forever-- so I want the lid to open up if I touch it.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.60,1:48:46.68,chinese,,0,0,0,,我希望一碰盖子，盖子就会打开。
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.68,1:48:49.27,english,,0,0,0,,So if the cursor gets near the lid, I want the lid to open up.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.68,1:48:49.27,chinese,,0,0,0,,就是说，如果光标靠近盖子，我就想让盖子打开。
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.27,1:48:51.34,english,,0,0,0,,And then if I move away, I want it to close.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.27,1:48:51.34,chinese,,0,0,0,,如果把光标拿开，我希望它能马上关闭。
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.34,1:48:52.64,english,,0,0,0,,So how can I do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.34,1:48:52.64,chinese,,0,0,0,,那我该怎么实现呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.64,1:48:59.20,english,,0,0,0,,I want an If, but I just don't want one question, I really want two, a fork in the road that goes left or right, so to speak.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.64,1:48:59.20,chinese,,0,0,0,,我想要一个 "if" 条件判断，但是延伸出两条路径，可以说是一个向左或向右的岔路口。
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.20,1:49:02.83,english,,0,0,0,,And let me grab this puzzle piece here, as I did long ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.20,1:49:02.83,chinese,,0,0,0,,让我像当初上学一样，抓住这块拼图。
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.83,1:49:04.69,english,,0,0,0,,So notice, it grows to fill.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.83,1:49:04.69,chinese,,0,0,0,,注意一下，它可以自动填充到合适的大小。
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.69,1:49:06.43,english,,0,0,0,,What's the question I want to ask?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.69,1:49:06.43,chinese,,0,0,0,,我想问什么问题？
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.43,1:49:13.86,english,,0,0,0,,Well, under Sensing, I'm going to go ahead here and say If this trashcan is Touching the Mouse Pointer-- what do I want to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.43,1:49:13.86,chinese,,0,0,0,,应该在 "感应 "功能下，我想问的是，如果鼠标指针碰到了这个垃圾桶，我该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.86,1:49:16.03,english,,0,0,0,,Well, I want to change what the trashcan looks like.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.86,1:49:16.03,chinese,,0,0,0,,我想改变垃圾桶的样子。
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.03,1:49:17.74,english,,0,0,0,,And this part, I did in advance of class.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.03,1:49:17.74,chinese,,0,0,0,,而这部分，我在课前就做好了。
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.74,1:49:21.04,english,,0,0,0,,If you go up here to Costumes, this is where all the graphical stuff happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.74,1:49:21.04,chinese,,0,0,0,,如果你进入 Customes 页面，所有导入的图片都会在这里展示。
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.04,1:49:31.42,english,,0,0,0,,And you'll see that I imported a whole bunch of different costumes that effectively, much like a video, when you play them quickly, creates the illusion of movement, some animation.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.04,1:49:31.42,chinese,,0,0,0,,你看到我导入了一大堆不同的服装，当你快速切换这些服装时，\N它们就像视频一样，能有效地营造出运动的错觉和一些动画效果。
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.42,1:49:35.32,english,,0,0,0,,But it's really just dot, dot, dot, dot, dot-- different images showing on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.42,1:49:35.32,chinese,,0,0,0,,但实际上，屏幕上显示的只是点（像素）、点、点、点、点——不同的图像而已。
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.32,1:49:39.25,english,,0,0,0,,Well, some of these costumes are called like Oscar1, Oscar2.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.32,1:49:39.25,chinese,,0,0,0,,其中一些服装被称为 Oscar1、Oscar2 。
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.25,1:49:40.81,english,,0,0,0,,Oscar1 is closed.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.25,1:49:40.81,chinese,,0,0,0,,Oscar1 是关着的垃圾桶。
Dialogue: 0,1:49:40.81,1:49:42.07,english,,0,0,0,,Oscar2 is open.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:40.81,1:49:42.07,chinese,,0,0,0,,Oscar 2 是开着的垃圾桶。
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.07,1:49:43.73,english,,0,0,0,,So let's just deal with those first.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.07,1:49:43.73,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以我们先解决垃圾桶的开关触发吧。
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.73,1:49:48.10,english,,0,0,0,,So if I'm touching the mouse pointer, let me go under-- how about Looks?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.73,1:49:48.10,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以，如果垃圾桶接触鼠标指针，让我切到下面外观栏。
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.10,1:49:50.68,english,,0,0,0,,And we didn't use this before, but there's this block,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.10,1:49:50.68,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们以前没有用过，但有这么个东西——
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.68,1:49:52.87,english,,0,0,0,,Switch Costume to Something Else.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.68,1:49:52.87,chinese,,0,0,0,,"改变服装到另一个"。
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.87,1:49:55.15,english,,0,0,0,,I'm going to drag and drop this inside of the If.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.87,1:49:55.15,chinese,,0,0,0,,我要把这个拖放到 if 块里面来。
Dialogue: 0,1:49:55.15,1:49:57.07,english,,0,0,0,,And notice it's a little bit indented.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:55.15,1:49:57.07,chinese,,0,0,0,,注意它有一点点缩进。
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.07,1:50:00.73,english,,0,0,0,,I'm going to change it not to Oscar8, but Oscar2.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.07,1:50:00.73,chinese,,0,0,0,,我要把它改成 Oscar2，而不是 Oscar8。
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.73,1:50:10.84,english,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, If Not Touching the Mouse Pointer-- this is the other direction in the fork in the road-- let's go ahead and switch the costume back to what I described as Oscar1.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.73,1:50:10.84,chinese,,0,0,0,,否则，如果垃圾桶没碰到鼠标指针—— 这是岔路口的另一个方向—— 我们得把服装换回 Oscar1。
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.84,1:50:12.40,english,,0,0,0,,So let me run this program.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.84,1:50:12.40,chinese,,0,0,0,,让我来运行下这个程序。
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.40,1:50:14.90,english,,0,0,0,,And not much of interest is happening yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.40,1:50:14.90,chinese,,0,0,0,,目前还没有什么值得注意的事情发生。
Dialogue: 0,1:50:14.90,1:50:20.03,english,,0,0,0,,But notice, if I move the cursor up, down-- but how is that working?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:14.90,1:50:20.03,chinese,,0,0,0,,但注意了，如果我将光标向上、向下... 但这是怎么做到的呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.03,1:50:22.94,english,,0,0,0,,It's just changing the costume that's being overlaid on the sprite.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.03,1:50:22.94,chinese,,0,0,0,,这只是在改变叠加在精灵上的服装。
Dialogue: 0,1:50:22.94,1:50:25.99,english,,0,0,0,,So it looks like interactivity, but you are really just changing the aesthetics.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:22.94,1:50:25.99,chinese,,0,0,0,,因此，这看起来像是在与垃圾桶交互，但实际上你只是在改变一些贴图。
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.99,1:50:29.13,english,,0,0,0,,And we humans are just kind of assuming, oh, it's opening up.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.99,1:50:29.13,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们人类就会想当然，哦，它正在打开。
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.13,1:50:30.76,english,,0,0,0,,Well, no, it's just changing a costume.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.13,1:50:30.76,chinese,,0,0,0,,嗯不，只是换一套服装。
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.76,1:50:31.80,english,,0,0,0,,So here's the difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.76,1:50:31.80,chinese,,0,0,0,,这就是区别所在。
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.80,1:50:34.21,english,,0,0,0,,The high-level abstraction-- trashcan opening.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.80,1:50:34.21,chinese,,0,0,0,,高级抽象—— 打开垃圾桶。
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.21,1:50:38.50,english,,0,0,0,,The lower-level implementation detail-- costume changing, creating that illusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.21,1:50:38.50,chinese,,0,0,0,,较低层次的实现细节—— 换装，营造幻觉。
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.50,1:50:46.13,english,,0,0,0,,And if I want it to look prettier, I could just have many other costumes and go boom, boom, boom, boom, boom to create more frames per second, if you will.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.50,1:50:46.13,chinese,,0,0,0,,如果我想让它看起来更美观，可以多导入一些服装，\N然后快速切换，在一秒内展示更多帧。
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.13,1:50:48.82,english,,0,0,0,,So I need to do one other thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.13,1:50:48.82,chinese,,0,0,0,,我还需要做一件事。
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.82,1:50:52.75,english,,0,0,0,,Maybe if I accidentally leave the trashcan open, let me make one change here.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.82,1:50:52.75,chinese,,0,0,0,,也许在最开始垃圾桶不小心打开了，让我在这里做一个改变。
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.75,1:50:54.73,english,,0,0,0,,Let me make sure that the very first thing
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.75,1:50:54.73,chinese,,0,0,0,,让我确保正确的初始化，
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.73,1:51:01.81,english,,0,0,0,,I do when the Green Flag is clicked, is always start with the trashcan closed because otherwise, you might accidentally leave it open.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.73,1:51:01.81,chinese,,0,0,0,,当点击绿旗时，我总是先关闭垃圾桶，避免它呈现打开状态。
Dialogue: 0,1:51:01.81,1:51:03.59,english,,0,0,0,,So this gets me into some default state.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:01.81,1:51:03.59,chinese,,0,0,0,,这样，我就初始化了一个默认状态。
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.59,1:51:08.13,english,,0,0,0,,So now it's always closed until I manually hover over it instead.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.59,1:51:08.13,chinese,,0,0,0,,因此现在它保持关闭，直到我手动将鼠标悬停在它上面。
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.13,1:51:09.55,english,,0,0,0,,Well, what might I have done next?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.13,1:51:09.55,chinese,,0,0,0,,那么，接下来我要干啥？
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.55,1:51:13.58,english,,0,0,0,,Well, if I wanted to introduce something like the trash, I need a second sprite.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.55,1:51:13.58,chinese,,0,0,0,,如果我想引入垃圾之类的东西，需要第二个精灵。
Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.58,1:51:15.67,english,,0,0,0,,And here, in advance, I grabbed the image already.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.58,1:51:15.67,chinese,,0,0,0,,在这里，我已经提前找好了图片。
Dialogue: 0,1:51:15.67,1:51:18.31,english,,0,0,0,,Let me pretend that this never happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:15.67,1:51:18.31,chinese,,0,0,0,,让我假装一下，从头来一遍。
Dialogue: 0,1:51:18.31,1:51:20.26,english,,0,0,0,,Let me drag this away here.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:18.31,1:51:20.26,chinese,,0,0,0,,把这个拖走。
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.26,1:51:24.03,english,,0,0,0,,And now I have nothing in my code area for this piece of trash.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.26,1:51:24.03,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在，我的代码区里没有关于垃圾的任何东西。
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.03,1:51:25.20,english,,0,0,0,,But it is the second sprite.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.03,1:51:25.20,chinese,,0,0,0,,垃圾是第二个精灵。
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.20,1:51:29.19,english,,0,0,0,,And all I did was I clicked on the little cat plus icon here, created a second sprite.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.20,1:51:29.19,chinese,,0,0,0,,我所做的就是点击这里的小猫加号图标，创建第二个精灵。
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.19,1:51:30.33,english,,0,0,0,,I named it trash.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.19,1:51:30.33,chinese,,0,0,0,,我把它命名为垃圾。
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.33,1:51:32.25,english,,0,0,0,,I added a costume for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.33,1:51:32.25,chinese,,0,0,0,,我为它添加了一套服装。
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.25,1:51:34.17,english,,0,0,0,,Sort of the aesthetic stuff, I did in advance.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.25,1:51:34.17,chinese,,0,0,0,,我提前做了一些提升美观度的工作。
Dialogue: 0,1:51:34.17,1:51:36.36,english,,0,0,0,,But here I'll do now the code.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:34.17,1:51:36.36,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在要完成代码部分。
Dialogue: 0,1:51:36.36,1:51:37.72,english,,0,0,0,,How do I want to do this?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:36.36,1:51:37.72,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们想要什么效果？
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.72,1:51:42.16,english,,0,0,0,,Well, how about when the Green Flag is clicked, for the trash can,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.72,1:51:42.16,chinese,,0,0,0,,点击绿旗后，垃圾桶就会出现，
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.16,1:51:45.09,english,,0,0,0,,I want the trash can in parallel to do--
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.16,1:51:45.09,chinese,,0,0,0,,我想让垃圾桶和垃圾并行地做自己的事情，
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.09,1:51:48.19,english,,0,0,0,,I want the trash, the piece of trash, to do its own thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.09,1:51:48.19,chinese,,0,0,0,,我想让垃圾自己往下掉。
Dialogue: 0,1:51:48.19,1:51:52.50,english,,0,0,0,,So what I want it to do is maybe let's do Motion, how about?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:48.19,1:51:52.50,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以，我想让它移动起来，怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,1:51:52.50,1:51:54.24,english,,0,0,0,,And let's go to a specific coordinate.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:52.50,1:51:54.24,chinese,,0,0,0,,让我们来看一个具体的坐标。
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.24,1:51:55.75,english,,0,0,0,,Now, there's a lot of options here.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.24,1:51:55.75,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在，这里有很多选择。
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.75,1:52:01.74,english,,0,0,0,,There's Turning, Go to a Random Position, Go to x,y, Glide, more elegantly.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.75,1:52:01.74,chinese,,0,0,0,,比如说 "转弯"、"转到随机位置"、"转到 x,y 坐标"、"滑行" 等等的优雅功能。
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.74,1:52:03.99,english,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of different ways to implement movement.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.74,1:52:03.99,chinese,,0,0,0,,有很多不同的方法来实现运动。
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.99,1:52:06.31,english,,0,0,0,,I just want it to go to a very specific location first.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.99,1:52:06.31,chinese,,0,0,0,,我只是想让它先到达一个确切的位置。
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.31,1:52:09.00,english,,0,0,0,,So I'm just going to go to x,y first.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.31,1:52:09.00,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以我打算让它到 x,y 坐标处。
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.00,1:52:14.47,english,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to say x, how about, will be-- let's not hardcode this.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.00,1:52:14.47,chinese,,0,0,0,,我看看 x 要设置为多少... 噢，我们还是不要硬编码好了。
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.47,1:52:18.12,english,,0,0,0,,Let's just have it be-- well, let's do it at 0, initially, and then 240.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.47,1:52:18.12,chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧，x 从 0 开始，然后 y 是 240。
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.12,1:52:23.41,english,,0,0,0,,So-- whoops-- let's do 0,240 so that this piece of trash always starts at the top middle of the screen.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.12,1:52:23.41,chinese,,0,0,0,,0,240 ，这样这块垃圾就总是出现在屏幕的中上部。
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.41,1:52:26.16,english,,0,0,0,,If you think back to that coordinate system, 0,0 is in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.41,1:52:26.16,chinese,,0,0,0,,如果你回想一下那个坐标系，0,0 在正中间。
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.16,1:52:28.23,english,,0,0,0,,240 is straight above it.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.16,1:52:28.23,chinese,,0,0,0,,240 在正顶上。
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.23,1:52:31.15,english,,0,0,0,,All right, now, after I do that, what do I want to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.23,1:52:31.15,chinese,,0,0,0,,好了现在，在做完这些之后，我还想做什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:31.15,1:52:34.98,english,,0,0,0,,Well, how about I control this thing by forever falling.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:31.15,1:52:34.98,chinese,,0,0,0,,我想控制让它永远下落。
Dialogue: 0,1:52:34.98,1:52:36.42,english,,0,0,0,,Now, how do I make the trash move?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:34.98,1:52:36.42,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在，我该如何让垃圾移动呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.42,1:52:38.01,english,,0,0,0,,We haven't seen this puzzle piece yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.42,1:52:38.01,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们还没看到有这块拼图。
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.01,1:52:42.39,english,,0,0,0,,But under Motion, the very first thing is called Move Some Number of Steps.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.01,1:52:42.39,chinese,,0,0,0,,但在 Motion 下，有个东西叫做 "移动一定步数"。
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.39,1:52:43.38,english,,0,0,0,,By default, it's 10.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.39,1:52:43.38,chinese,,0,0,0,,默认值为 10。
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.38,1:52:44.88,english,,0,0,0,,But we'll do it more simply.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.38,1:52:44.88,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们简单点就行了。
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.88,1:52:48.66,english,,0,0,0,,Let me go ahead and move-- oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.88,1:52:48.66,chinese,,0,0,0,,接着看，等等...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.66,1:52:52.35,english,,0,0,0,,Move is going to move it in whatever direction it's facing.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.66,1:52:52.35,chinese,,0,0,0,,Move 会让它朝自己面向的方向运动。
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.35,1:52:53.75,english,,0,0,0,,I only want it to move down.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.35,1:52:53.75,chinese,,0,0,0,,可我只想让它向下移动。
Dialogue: 0,1:52:53.75,1:52:57.54,english,,0,0,0,,So here, even I'm getting confused as to how many different ways there are to do things.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:53.75,1:52:57.54,chinese,,0,0,0,,在 Scratch，连我自己都搞不清楚到底有多少种不同的方法。
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.54,1:52:59.68,english,,0,0,0,,What I thing I want to do is this.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.54,1:52:59.68,chinese,,0,0,0,,我想做的事情是这样的。
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.68,1:53:03.67,english,,0,0,0,,Let me only change my y-axis as follows.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.68,1:53:03.67,chinese,,0,0,0,,我只想要对 y 轴的坐标做改动。
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.67,1:53:06.06,english,,0,0,0,,So here's another puzzle piece called Change y.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.67,1:53:06.06,chinese,,0,0,0,,这里还有一块拼图，叫做 "变化 y"。
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.06,1:53:07.68,english,,0,0,0,,So again, y is the vertical.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.06,1:53:07.68,chinese,,0,0,0,,再说一遍，y 是垂直方向。
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.68,1:53:14.17,english,,0,0,0,,So let me just change y by one pixel downward at a time, so -1 one pixel at a time.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.68,1:53:14.17,chinese,,0,0,0,,设置每次向下改变一个像素，也就是每次让 y -1。
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.17,1:53:15.54,english,,0,0,0,,So it's kind of slow.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.17,1:53:15.54,chinese,,0,0,0,,有点慢。
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.54,1:53:17.01,english,,0,0,0,,And I think now--
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.54,1:53:17.01,chinese,,0,0,0,,我想想啊现在，
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.01,1:53:17.89,english,,0,0,0,,I think that's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.01,1:53:17.89,chinese,,0,0,0,,差不多就完事了。
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.89,1:53:18.99,english,,0,0,0,,Let me hit Stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.89,1:53:18.99,chinese,,0,0,0,,让我先停止现在的。
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.99,1:53:21.70,english,,0,0,0,,Notice that my trashcan is still going to be interactive.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.99,1:53:21.70,chinese,,0,0,0,,请注意，垃圾桶仍将是可以交互的。
Dialogue: 0,1:53:21.70,1:53:23.37,english,,0,0,0,,I haven't changed or deleted that code.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:21.70,1:53:23.37,chinese,,0,0,0,,我没有更改或删除这部分代码。
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.37,1:53:26.85,english,,0,0,0,,I've just added now code for my piece of trash.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.37,1:53:26.85,chinese,,0,0,0,,只是为垃圾添加了新代码。
Dialogue: 0,1:53:26.85,1:53:32.92,english,,0,0,0,,If I click the Green Flag, notice that-- after I enable it-- let me start that again.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:26.85,1:53:32.92,chinese,,0,0,0,,如果我点开始，请看—— 我得先让它可见，再重新开始。
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.92,1:53:34.32,english,,0,0,0,,I had it hidden for before class.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.92,1:53:34.32,chinese,,0,0,0,,刚才上课点了下隐藏。
Dialogue: 0,1:53:34.32,1:53:35.40,english,,0,0,0,,But let me enable it now--
Dialogue: 0,1:53:34.32,1:53:35.40,chinese,,0,0,0,,不过现在要开启了。
Dialogue: 0,1:53:35.40,1:53:42.75,english,,0,0,0,,Green Flag, notice it starts dead center, at x equals 0, y equals 240, and it's dropping one pixel at a time.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:35.40,1:53:42.75,chinese,,0,0,0,,开始，注意它是从上面的正中心出现的，x 等于 0，y 等于 240，每次下降一个像素。
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.75,1:53:47.53,english,,0,0,0,,If that seems a little boring, we can change it to -10 pixels at a time and, boom, it's done.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.75,1:53:47.53,chinese,,0,0,0,,如果这看起来有点无聊，我们可以把它改成每次 -10 像素，然后，砰的一下它就完成了。
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.53,1:53:49.78,english,,0,0,0,,So that's how you might change the speed of a program.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.53,1:53:49.78,chinese,,0,0,0,,这就是改变速度的方式。
Dialogue: 0,1:53:49.78,1:53:51.75,english,,0,0,0,,But I'm going to leave it more simply as -1.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:49.78,1:53:51.75,chinese,,0,0,0,,不过我还是把它调回 -1。
Dialogue: 0,1:53:51.75,1:53:54.70,english,,0,0,0,,And honestly, it would be nice if it doesn't always start from the top.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:51.75,1:53:54.70,chinese,,0,0,0,,老实说，如果垃圾不总是从那里出现，那就更好了。
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.70,1:53:57.08,english,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, this game is not going to be very interactive.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.70,1:53:57.08,chinese,,0,0,0,,否则，这个游戏的互动性就不会很强。
Dialogue: 0,1:53:57.08,1:54:00.58,english,,0,0,0,,I'm literally going to be grabbing the trash from the same place every time.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:57.08,1:54:00.58,chinese,,0,0,0,,我每次都要从同一个地方抓垃圾，这简直了。
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.58,1:54:03.25,english,,0,0,0,,So why don't I, instead, Stop this.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.58,1:54:03.25,chinese,,0,0,0,,为什么不试试呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:54:03.25,1:54:06.55,english,,0,0,0,,Let me go under Operators, and let's pick a random number.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:03.25,1:54:06.55,chinese,,0,0,0,,让我在 Operators 类别下，找到 "随机选取一个数字"。
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.55,1:54:12.43,english,,0,0,0,,So let me change the hardcoded-- the manually inputted-- 0, and let's make x be somewhere between 0
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.55,1:54:12.43,chinese,,0,0,0,,因此，让我丢掉刚才的硬编码，手动输入的 0，让 x 介于 0 和某个值之间
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.43,1:54:20.97,english,,0,0,0,,so in the middle and all the way over to-- what was it-- oh, I got my numbers wrong-- 240 and my y will be 180.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.43,1:54:20.97,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以从中间一直到... 啥来着... 哦，我把数字弄错了，是 240，这个 y 应该是 180。
Dialogue: 0,1:54:20.97,1:54:23.56,english,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I got my x and my y confused.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:20.97,1:54:23.56,chinese,,0,0,0,,不好意思，我把 x 和 y 搞混了。
Dialogue: 0,1:54:23.56,1:54:25.42,english,,0,0,0,,So let me play this again.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:23.56,1:54:25.42,chinese,,0,0,0,,让我再启动一遍。
Dialogue: 0,1:54:25.42,1:54:30.97,english,,0,0,0,,And now we have a game that's more like games you might have played growing up or even now, like there's some randomness to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:25.42,1:54:30.97,chinese,,0,0,0,,而现在，我们的游戏更像你先前玩过的游戏，带有一些随机性。
Dialogue: 0,1:54:30.97,1:54:33.66,english,,0,0,0,,So the CPU, so to speak, is doing something more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:30.97,1:54:33.66,chinese,,0,0,0,,可以说，CPU 正在做一些更有趣的事情。
Dialogue: 0,1:54:33.66,1:54:34.57,english,,0,0,0,,Let me run it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:33.66,1:54:34.57,chinese,,0,0,0,,我再来跑一遍。
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.57,1:54:35.82,english,,0,0,0,,Now it's a little to the left.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.57,1:54:35.82,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在比刚才更偏左。
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.82,1:54:36.60,english,,0,0,0,,Let me run it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.82,1:54:36.60,chinese,,0,0,0,,再跑一遍。
Dialogue: 0,1:54:36.60,1:54:38.05,english,,0,0,0,,Now it's a little more to the left.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:36.60,1:54:38.05,chinese,,0,0,0,,往左移了一点。
Dialogue: 0,1:54:38.05,1:54:39.63,english,,0,0,0,,Again-- now it's back to the right.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:38.05,1:54:39.63,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在又回到右边一些了。
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.63,1:54:41.64,english,,0,0,0,,So randomness just makes games more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.63,1:54:41.64,chinese,,0,0,0,,因此，随机性可以让游戏更有趣。
Dialogue: 0,1:54:41.64,1:54:46.17,english,,0,0,0,,And this is why when you play any video game, if different things are happening, there's probably just some randomness.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:41.64,1:54:46.17,chinese,,0,0,0,,这就是为什么你玩的几乎任何电子游戏，都带点不同性和随机性。
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.17,1:54:48.36,english,,0,0,0,,And it's quantized as just a simple number.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.17,1:54:48.36,chinese,,0,0,0,,随机性被量化为一个简简单单的数字。
Dialogue: 0,1:54:48.36,1:54:52.05,english,,0,0,0,,Now, I think I just need one final flourish here, if I may.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:48.36,1:54:52.05,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在，我想需要在这里做最后的铺垫。
Dialogue: 0,1:54:52.05,1:54:54.06,english,,0,0,0,,Let me go ahead and add this.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:52.05,1:54:54.06,chinese,,0,0,0,,让我来补充一下。
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.06,1:54:58.38,english,,0,0,0,,How about Events-- or rather-- yes, Events.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.06,1:54:58.38,chinese,,0,0,0,,那 "事件" 呢？ 这里的 Events。
Dialogue: 0,1:54:58.38,1:55:02.70,english,,0,0,0,,When Green Flag is clicked, I can do multiple things within the same sprite.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:58.38,1:55:02.70,chinese,,0,0,0,,当点击绿旗时，我可以在同一个精灵上同时执行几个操作。
Dialogue: 0,1:55:02.70,1:55:05.19,english,,0,0,0,,They don't all have to be attached to the same one.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:02.70,1:55:05.19,chinese,,0,0,0,,它们不一定都要连接到同一个 "when green flag clicked" 块上。
Dialogue: 0,1:55:05.19,1:55:10.11,english,,0,0,0,,Let me go ahead and forever go ahead and do something else.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:05.19,1:55:10.11,chinese,,0,0,0,,我再建一个，拖过来 forever 循环做点别的事。
Dialogue: 0,1:55:10.11,1:55:20.85,english,,0,0,0,,How about, Whenever the Trash is-- how about-- Touching the Trash Can-- so Forever If-- let's see, I need a Sensing block.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:10.11,1:55:20.85,chinese,,0,0,0,,不如来个 "每当垃圾触碰垃圾桶，就..."
Dialogue: 0,1:55:20.85,1:55:28.53,english,,0,0,0,,So how about, Is Touching-- not the Mouse Pointer, this time, but Touching Oscar himself there.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:20.85,1:55:28.53,chinese,,0,0,0,,那么，需要一个 touching 块，这次不选择鼠标指针了，而是 "触摸 Oscar"。
Dialogue: 0,1:55:28.53,1:55:30.81,english,,0,0,0,,Now let's see what happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:28.53,1:55:30.81,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在让我们看看会发生什么。
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.81,1:55:33.75,english,,0,0,0,,All right, so let's go ahead and click the Green Flag.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.81,1:55:33.75,chinese,,0,0,0,,好了，让我们点点绿旗。
Dialogue: 0,1:55:33.75,1:55:37.56,english,,0,0,0,,Now I go down over here and let go.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:33.75,1:55:37.56,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在，我把垃圾抓下来，然后放手。
Dialogue: 0,1:55:37.56,1:55:41.34,english,,0,0,0,,OK, I kind of want it to go into the trash can.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:37.56,1:55:41.34,chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧，我其实有点想把它扔进垃圾桶。
Dialogue: 0,1:55:41.34,1:55:43.62,english,,0,0,0,,How do I make it go into the trash can?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:41.34,1:55:43.62,chinese,,0,0,0,,怎样才能把它扔进垃圾桶？
Dialogue: 0,1:55:43.62,1:55:49.95,english,,0,0,0,,How can we take this high-level idea, put trash into the trash can, and make it seem to disappear?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:43.62,1:55:49.95,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们怎样才能从底层实现这个高层次的想法——扔进垃圾桶，让它看起来消失不见？
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.95,1:55:51.52,english,,0,0,0,,Logically, what could we do?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.95,1:55:51.52,chinese,,0,0,0,,从逻辑上讲，我们要怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.52,1:55:52.37,english,,0,0,0,,Yeah--
Dialogue: 0,1:55:52.37,1:55:53.24,english,,0,0,0,,AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE]
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.24,1:55:56.03,english,,0,0,0,,DAVID J. MALAN: OK, so when it touches it, let's have it disappear.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.24,1:55:56.03,chinese,,0,0,0,,对的，当它俩碰到的时候，让垃圾消失。
Dialogue: 0,1:55:56.03,1:55:56.91,english,,0,0,0,,So I could hide it.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:56.03,1:55:56.91,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们可以把它藏起来。
Dialogue: 0,1:55:56.91,1:56:04.38,english,,0,0,0,,Or honestly, if the game is going to be ongoing, like it was, letting me drop more and more trash, let me just have it go ahead and pick a new random location.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:56.91,1:56:04.38,chinese,,0,0,0,,如果游戏要持续下去，就像演示那样，\N需要扔下越来越多的垃圾，那就让它继续随机选择一个新的地点再次出现吧。
Dialogue: 0,1:56:04.38,1:56:05.56,english,,0,0,0,,So let me do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:04.38,1:56:05.56,chinese,,0,0,0,,我来试试
Dialogue: 0,1:56:05.56,1:56:09.07,english,,0,0,0,,Let me go ahead and Copy this puzzle piece up here and Duplicate.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:05.56,1:56:09.07,chinese,,0,0,0,,我想复制这块拼图。
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.07,1:56:10.74,english,,0,0,0,,And I don't want the whole thing, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.07,1:56:10.74,chinese,,0,0,0,,我不想要这一整块，不好意思。
Dialogue: 0,1:56:10.74,1:56:12.40,english,,0,0,0,,Let me get rid of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:10.74,1:56:12.40,chinese,,0,0,0,,把这个扔掉。
Dialogue: 0,1:56:12.40,1:56:13.54,english,,0,0,0,,Let me just do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:12.40,1:56:13.54,chinese,,0,0,0,,挪过来。
Dialogue: 0,1:56:13.54,1:56:16.72,english,,0,0,0,,Let me go back to some random location at the top.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:13.54,1:56:16.72,chinese,,0,0,0,,让垃圾回到顶部的某个随机位置。
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.72,1:56:17.94,english,,0,0,0,,So now notice what happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.72,1:56:17.94,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在请注意发生了什么。
Dialogue: 0,1:56:17.94,1:56:26.31,english,,0,0,0,,If I click and drag on it-- here it goes-- and I let go, it looks like it's going into the trash can because it snaps back up to some random location.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:17.94,1:56:26.31,chinese,,0,0,0,,如果我点击并拖动它，然后松手，\N它看起来就像被扔进垃圾桶，因为它实际是随机地弹回到某个初始位置。
Dialogue: 0,1:56:26.31,1:56:29.61,english,,0,0,0,,Now, the only thing I'm not doing really is keeping track of any kind of score.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:26.31,1:56:29.61,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在，我唯一没有做的事情就是记分。
Dialogue: 0,1:56:29.61,1:56:33.94,english,,0,0,0,,And it turns out, if I full screen this, it's not going to be draggable, by default.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:29.61,1:56:33.94,chinese,,0,0,0,,事实证明，如果我全屏显示，默认情况下它是不可拖动的。
Dialogue: 0,1:56:33.94,1:56:45.96,english,,0,0,0,,So just as a corner case, so to speak, something that you might trip over otherwise, let me go ahead and under, let's see, Sensing, it turns out I also need this for the piece of trash.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:33.94,1:56:45.96,chinese,,0,0,0,,这算是一个边界条件，你可能会被卡住。\N让我们看看，Sensing 里面，原来我还需要设置这个垃圾桶...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:45.96,1:56:51.54,english,,0,0,0,,There's this way of setting, in Scratch, a sprite to be draggable or not draggable.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:45.96,1:56:51.54,chinese,,0,0,0,,在 Scratch 中，可以设置精灵是否可拖动。
Dialogue: 0,1:56:51.54,1:57:00.24,english,,0,0,0,,I need to explicitly make it draggable so that when I do full screen this thing now, it still remains draggable and someone like myself can play it again and again.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:51.54,1:57:00.24,chinese,,0,0,0,,我需要明确规定它是可拖动的，这样当我现在全屏显示这个东西时，\N它仍然是可拖动的，多试几次都行。
Dialogue: 0,1:57:00.24,1:57:03.12,english,,0,0,0,,Well, how about we supplement this with one final flourish?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:00.24,1:57:03.12,chinese,,0,0,0,,那么，我们最后再锦上添花一下如何？
Dialogue: 0,1:57:03.12,1:57:06.01,english,,0,0,0,,Why don't we keep track now of the user score?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:03.12,1:57:06.01,chinese,,0,0,0,,为什么我们现在不记录玩家得分？
Dialogue: 0,1:57:06.01,1:57:16.59,english,,0,0,0,,So how about, when the user actually drags the piece of trash to the trash can, let me go under Variables here, where, in advance, I've already made myself a variable called Score.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:06.01,1:57:16.59,chinese,,0,0,0,,当玩家真的把垃圾拖到垃圾桶时，让我提前在变量栏下，创建一个 score 变量。
Dialogue: 0,1:57:16.59,1:57:20.10,english,,0,0,0,,I could have called it x or y or z or ABC, but that's not very descriptive.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:16.59,1:57:20.10,chinese,,0,0,0,,我本可以把它叫做 x、y、z 或 ABC，但这样太不贴切了。
Dialogue: 0,1:57:20.10,1:57:24.45,english,,0,0,0,,In programming, you typically give things a more descriptive English, or some other language, name.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:20.10,1:57:24.45,chinese,,0,0,0,,在编程过程中，你通常会给东西起一个描述性的英文名称。
Dialogue: 0,1:57:24.45,1:57:26.20,english,,0,0,0,,So I called this one Score.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:24.45,1:57:26.20,chinese,,0,0,0,,因此，我把这个变量命名为 score。
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.20,1:57:28.71,english,,0,0,0,,So how do I want to do this in my Score?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.20,1:57:28.71,chinese,,0,0,0,,那我要怎么让 score 显示出得分呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.71,1:57:37.47,english,,0,0,0,,Well, let me go ahead and initially set this game score to 0 at the very top of one of these scripts-- one of these programs up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.71,1:57:37.47,chinese,,0,0,0,,接着整，在这些代码的最顶端将 score 设置为 0，在一个地方设置就行了。
Dialogue: 0,1:57:37.47,1:57:42.57,english,,0,0,0,,And then any time my piece of trash is touching
Dialogue: 0,1:57:37.47,1:57:42.57,chinese,,0,0,0,,每当垃圾被碰到时，
Dialogue: 0,1:57:42.57,1:57:49.63,english,,0,0,0,,Oscar, let's not just jump to the top, let's change the score by 1 up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:42.57,1:57:49.63,chinese,,0,0,0,,对于 Oscar，我们不要直接跳到最上面，先在这里把 score 增加 1。
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.63,1:57:52.68,english,,0,0,0,,So now notice, If Touching Oscar, Change the Score-- that is,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.63,1:57:52.68,chinese,,0,0,0,,"如果触碰到 Oscar，就增加 score" ，就是这个意思，
Dialogue: 0,1:57:52.68,1:57:55.92,english,,0,0,0,,Add 1 to the Score-- and then Pick a new Random location.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:52.68,1:57:55.92,chinese,,0,0,0,,让 score 加 1，然后选择一个新的随机位置。
Dialogue: 0,1:57:55.92,1:57:59.52,english,,0,0,0,,And now Green Flag-- let's do this slowly.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:55.92,1:57:59.52,chinese,,0,0,0,,点下绿旗，我们慢慢看。
Dialogue: 0,1:57:59.52,1:58:00.54,english,,0,0,0,,Here it goes.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:59.52,1:58:00.54,chinese,,0,0,0,,开始了。
Dialogue: 0,1:58:00.54,1:58:01.59,english,,0,0,0,,The trashcan opens.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:00.54,1:58:01.59,chinese,,0,0,0,,垃圾桶打开了。
Dialogue: 0,1:58:01.59,1:58:02.52,english,,0,0,0,,I let go.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:02.52,1:58:06.66,english,,0,0,0,,And now notice, at the top left of my program, notice the score is now 2.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:02.52,1:58:06.66,chinese,,0,0,0,,注意看程序的左上角，score 现在是 2。
Dialogue: 0,1:58:06.66,1:58:10.14,english,,0,0,0,,Notice the score, if I do this again, is about to become 3.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:06.66,1:58:10.14,chinese,,0,0,0,,如果我再做一次，score 就要变成 3 了。
Dialogue: 0,1:58:10.14,1:58:15.91,english,,0,0,0,,And so here we have building blocks, literally, of making this program better and better and better.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:10.14,1:58:15.91,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以我们在不断地添砖加瓦，让这个程序越来越棒。
Dialogue: 0,1:58:15.91,1:58:22.53,english,,0,0,0,,And so, indeed, that's how you generally approach solving any problem with code, be it in Scratch or C or Python or some other.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:15.91,1:58:22.53,chinese,,0,0,0,,因此，不管是用 Scratch、C、Python 还是其他语言，\N用代码解决任何问题时，一般都是这个过程。
Dialogue: 0,1:58:22.53,1:58:31.53,english,,0,0,0,,You take this vision you might have or some vision you've been assigned in a homework assignment and try to break it down into these constituent parts and just pluck off the easy ones first.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:22.53,1:58:31.53,chinese,,0,0,0,,你要把自己的想法，或家庭作业中布置给你的要求，\N分解成不同的部分，先把容易的部分做出来。
Dialogue: 0,1:58:31.53,1:58:34.98,english,,0,0,0,,Put the lamp post there first, and at least feel like you're making some progress.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:31.53,1:58:34.98,chinese,,0,0,0,,像我先把灯柱放在那儿，至少会让人觉得你取得了一些进展。
Dialogue: 0,1:58:34.98,1:58:38.45,english,,0,0,0,,Then pluck off something like the trash can, and just make it do a little thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:34.98,1:58:38.45,chinese,,0,0,0,,然后拖来垃圾桶之类的东西，让它有简单的行为。
Dialogue: 0,1:58:38.45,1:58:40.54,english,,0,0,0,,And it doesn't have to be in some same order here.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:38.45,1:58:40.54,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们做的顺序不一定要相同。
Dialogue: 0,1:58:40.54,1:58:42.75,english,,0,0,0,,I could have done this in a million different ways.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:40.54,1:58:42.75,chinese,,0,0,0,,完成这个程序亦有无数种方式。
Dialogue: 0,1:58:42.75,1:58:52.38,english,,0,0,0,,But figure out what the small pieces are that, ultimately, like a few of the problems we've solved today, assemble into a greater solution there too.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:42.75,1:58:52.38,chinese,,0,0,0,,只要想清楚，这些小碎片最终会像我们今天解决的几个问题一样，组合成一个更完善的解决方案。
Dialogue: 0,1:58:52.38,1:58:58.47,english,,0,0,0,,So that you have now a mental model for these types of blocks and others, let's return for a moment to this.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:52.38,1:58:58.47,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在你已经初步建立关于这些类型的积木的思维模式，让我们再回顾一下。
Dialogue: 0,1:58:58.47,1:59:06.67,english,,0,0,0,,We saw a moment ago that when I started saying, "Hello, David," and nesting those puzzle pieces, we had a whole different paradigm altogether.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:58.47,1:59:06.67,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们刚刚看到，当我开始说 "Hello, David"，\N并嵌套这些积木时，我们有了一个有点新奇的思维模式。
Dialogue: 0,1:59:06.67,1:59:15.00,english,,0,0,0,,My input for that second version of, "Hello, world," was to now pass in, for instance, "What's Your Name?" into my function, called Ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:06.67,1:59:15.00,chinese,,0,0,0,,第二个版本的 "Hello, world" 的输入，是先将 "What's Your Name?" 传递给 Ask 函数...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:15.00,1:59:21.69,english,,0,0,0,,That gave me not a side effect, but what I called, again, a return value, called Answer, by default, in Scratch.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:15.00,1:59:21.69,chinese,,0,0,0,,这没有产生副作用，而是有一个返回值，Scratch 默认称之为 answer。
Dialogue: 0,1:59:21.69,1:59:31.26,english,,0,0,0,,And now notice and recall, when I had that same output become the input to my next block, it looked a little something like this--
Dialogue: 0,1:59:21.69,1:59:31.26,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在请注意并回想一下，当我把 ask 函数的输出 answer，\N变成下一个函数的输入时，它看起来有点像这样——
Dialogue: 0,1:59:31.26,1:59:32.10,english,,0,0,0,,Say.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:32.10,1:59:37.71,english,,0,0,0,,So how does this type of block and this nesting, this stacking of blocks, fit into the same mental model?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:32.10,1:59:37.71,chinese,,0,0,0,,积木相互嵌套堆叠，但归根结底是同一种思维模式。
Dialogue: 0,1:59:32.10,1:59:37.71,annotation,,0,0,0,,*注：思维模式指，接受输入、函数中进行算法运算、最终得到输出，这个过程。
Dialogue: 0,1:59:37.71,1:59:47.19,english,,0,0,0,,Well, same idea-- my input for that part of the story is now taking in not one input but two-- two arguments-- "hello" and the answer from before.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:37.71,1:59:47.19,chinese,,0,0,0,,同样的想法—— 对于这个 join 函数，它的输入不是单个，而是两个参数—— "hello" 和 询问名字，我们输入的 answer 变量。
Dialogue: 0,1:59:47.19,1:59:50.01,english,,0,0,0,,The function, in this case, is that new block called Join.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:47.19,1:59:50.01,chinese,,0,0,0,,在这种情况下，函数是那个叫做 join 的新积木。
Dialogue: 0,1:59:50.01,2:00:00.84,english,,0,0,0,,The output thereof is, "Hello, David," which itself became-- if we sort of animate this-- the input to my final function, which indeed was still Say.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:50.01,2:00:00.84,chinese,,0,0,0,,其输出是 "Hello, David"，这个输出又成为了最终函数 Say 的输入。
Dialogue: 0,2:00:00.84,2:00:06.72,english,,0,0,0,,And this is only to say-- no pun intended-- that almost everything that you do with these puzzle pieces
Dialogue: 0,2:00:00.84,2:00:06.72,chinese,,0,0,0,,这只是说，在无意间，几乎你使用这些积木做的所有事情，
Dialogue: 0,2:00:06.72,2:00:16.32,english,,0,0,0,,be it in the context of Oscartime or the mole whacking or even just something simple like, "Hello, world," will ultimately fit into that relatively simple mental model there.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:06.72,2:00:16.32,chinese,,0,0,0,,无论是在 Oscartime 、打地鼠游戏，还是仅仅是像 "Hello, world" 这样的简单程序，\N最终都满足这个理解上去很简单的思维模式。
Dialogue: 0,2:00:06.72,2:00:16.32,annotation,,0,0,0,,*注：思维模式指，接受 0 个或多个输入，函数中进行算法运算，最终得到输出或是副作用。程序就是这个过程的不断嵌套。
Dialogue: 0,2:00:16.32,2:00:20.22,english,,0,0,0,,Now, I thought we'd end by taking a look at just a couple of final examples.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:16.32,2:00:20.22,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们最后再看几个例子。
Dialogue: 0,2:00:20.22,2:00:22.95,english,,0,0,0,,These ones, too, made by some of your predecessors.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:20.22,2:00:22.95,chinese,,0,0,0,,这些也是上过 CS50 课程的前辈的作品。
Dialogue: 0,2:00:22.95,2:00:27.76,english,,0,0,0,,And for this, I thought we would not write code together, but read it instead.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:22.95,2:00:27.76,chinese,,0,0,0,,对这些程序，我想不用一起写一遍代码了，但是要读一读他们是怎么写的。
Dialogue: 0,2:00:27.76,2:00:36.72,english,,0,0,0,,And so allow me to open up one other example here that will show us a few different versions of a program that a predecessor made.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:27.76,2:00:36.72,chinese,,0,0,0,,我想在这里打开另一个例子，展示一下前人制作的程序的几个不同版本。
Dialogue: 0,2:00:36.72,2:00:38.34,english,,0,0,0,,Give me just a moment here.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:36.72,2:00:38.34,chinese,,0,0,0,,稍微等一等。
Dialogue: 0,2:00:38.34,2:00:42.96,english,,0,0,0,,And we'll see how we might build up to something even more interactive.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:38.34,2:00:42.96,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们来看看如何让程序更有互动性。
Dialogue: 0,2:00:42.96,2:00:51.09,english,,0,0,0,,And in just a moment, we'll see something they called Ivy's Hardest Game, focused here on these particular mechanics.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:42.96,2:00:51.09,chinese,,0,0,0,,稍后，我们将看到 "常春藤最难游戏"，重点是观察其中的特殊机制。
Dialogue: 0,2:00:51.09,2:00:58.56,english,,0,0,0,,So here is version 0, so to speak, of this program, wherein the goal was to create a game where you have to get out of some kind of maze.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:51.09,2:00:58.56,chinese,,0,0,0,,这是这个程序的第 0 版，这个游戏的目标是走出迷宫。
Dialogue: 0,2:00:58.56,2:01:01.80,english,,0,0,0,,And you have to get out, in this case, the Harvard crest from this maze.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:58.56,2:01:01.80,chinese,,0,0,0,,你要带领哈佛大学的校徽从这个迷宫中走出。
Dialogue: 0,2:01:01.80,2:01:08.04,english,,0,0,0,,Let me go ahead and just hit Play on this Green Flag so you can see what the first building block for this program might have been.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:01.80,2:01:08.04,chinese,,0,0,0,,我来按下开始键，就能看到这个程序的初版是什么样子了。
Dialogue: 0,2:01:08.04,2:01:12.99,english,,0,0,0,,Notice that my hand here is actually on the Arrow keys on my keyboard.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:08.04,2:01:12.99,chinese,,0,0,0,,请注意，我的手是放在键盘的方向键上的。
Dialogue: 0,2:01:12.99,2:01:20.43,english,,0,0,0,,And it seems that by moving up, down, left, or right, this little crest on the screen responds in exactly that way.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:12.99,2:01:20.43,chinese,,0,0,0,,似乎只要上下左右移动，屏幕上的这个小徽章就会跟着反应。
Dialogue: 0,2:01:20.43,2:01:22.14,english,,0,0,0,,Now, let's hypothesize for just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:20.43,2:01:22.14,chinese,,0,0,0,,现在，让我们猜想一下。
Dialogue: 0,2:01:22.14,2:01:27.26,english,,0,0,0,,Even though we've not done anything quite like this before, how might this code be implemented?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:22.14,2:01:27.26,chinese,,0,0,0,,尽管我们以前没有做过类似的任务，这种代码要如何实现呢？
Dialogue: 0,2:01:27.26,2:01:34.22,english,,0,0,0,,How do you get a sprite, be it a cat or a crest, to respond to keys on a keyboard-- might you think intuitively?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:27.26,2:01:34.22,chinese,,0,0,0,,如何让一个精灵（无论是猫还是徽章）对键盘上的按键做出反应，你能用直觉想一想吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:01:34.22,2:01:34.73,english,,0,0,0,,Yeah--
Dialogue: 0,2:01:34.73,2:01:36.98,english,,0,0,0,,AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE]
Dialogue: 0,2:01:36.98,2:01:40.41,english,,0,0,0,,DAVID J. MALAN: Yeah, there could be something sensing what key you're pressing on.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:36.98,2:01:40.41,chinese,,0,0,0,,是的，可能有什么东西，能感应到你按的是什么键。
Dialogue: 0,2:01:40.41,2:01:44.60,english,,0,0,0,,And if you do it again in forever a loop, you'll just constantly be listening for keystrokes.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:40.41,2:01:44.60,chinese,,0,0,0,,把这个操作放在一个 forever 循环里面，其实就在不间断地监听按键。
Dialogue: 0,2:01:44.60,2:01:47.24,english,,0,0,0,,And this is how, like, every piece of software nowadays works.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:44.60,2:01:47.24,chinese,,0,0,0,,如今，每款软件都是这样运行的。
Dialogue: 0,2:01:47.24,2:01:51.69,english,,0,0,0,,It's constantly waiting for your phone to be tapped or something to be typed on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:47.24,2:01:51.69,chinese,,0,0,0,,它一直在等待你轻触手机或在屏幕上输入内容。
Dialogue: 0,2:01:51.69,2:01:55.40,english,,0,0,0,,So let me go ahead and look inside of this existing program here.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:51.69,2:01:55.40,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以，我们先来看看这个程序的内部模样。
Dialogue: 0,2:01:55.40,2:01:59.73,english,,0,0,0,,And there's more going on, but we'll take a quick glance what's actually going on.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:55.40,2:01:59.73,chinese,,0,0,0,,只展示一部分，我们快速浏览一下实际情况就好。
Dialogue: 0,2:01:59.73,2:02:04.85,english,,0,0,0,,Well, up here at top left, notice, we just have Go To x Equals 0 and y Equals 0.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:59.73,2:02:04.85,chinese,,0,0,0,,注意看左上方，这里有 "移动到 x 0 和 y 0"。
Dialogue: 0,2:02:04.85,2:02:07.85,english,,0,0,0,,That means put the Harvard crest dead center in the middle of the stage.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:04.85,2:02:07.85,chinese,,0,0,0,,也就是说，把哈佛大学的校徽放在舞台的正中间。
Dialogue: 0,2:02:07.85,2:02:13.13,english,,0,0,0,,Then we have Forever two functions that we made in advance as custom functions--
Dialogue: 0,2:02:07.85,2:02:13.13,chinese,,0,0,0,,然后，这里有两个自定义函数，分别是
Dialogue: 0,2:02:13.13,2:02:15.50,english,,0,0,0,,Listen for Keyboard, Feel for Walls.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:13.13,2:02:15.50,chinese,,0,0,0,,监听键盘按键，感知墙壁。
Dialogue: 0,2:02:15.50,2:02:17.19,english,,0,0,0,,So it's doing two things at once.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:15.50,2:02:17.19,chinese,,0,0,0,,因此，它同时在做两件事。
Dialogue: 0,2:02:17.19,2:02:23.27,english,,0,0,0,,It's forever listening for the keyboard-- up, down, left, right-- and feeling for the walls, in the sense that if I get too far to the left,
Dialogue: 0,2:02:17.19,2:02:23.27,chinese,,0,0,0,,首先它一直在监听玩家按下键盘的方向键，并做出对应的行动，\N还有感知墙壁以免角色穿墙而过。
Dialogue: 0,2:02:23.27,2:02:26.01,english,,0,0,0,,I don't want it to keep moving past that black wall.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:23.27,2:02:26.01,chinese,,0,0,0,,我们不想让它穿过那堵黑墙。
Dialogue: 0,2:02:26.01,2:02:29.06,english,,0,0,0,,And if it moves too far to the right, I don't want it to blow through that wall either.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:26.01,2:02:29.06,chinese,,0,0,0,,如果它一直向右，也不想让它撞穿右边那堵墙。
Dialogue: 0,2:02:29.06,2:02:34.25,english,,0,0,0,,So it's going to do two things constantly, listening for keyboard and feeling for walls, so to speak.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:29.06,2:02:34.25,chinese,,0,0,0,,因此，它要不断循环做两件事：监听键盘和感知墙壁。
Dialogue: 0,2:02:34.25,2:02:35.87,english,,0,0,0,,And how are those implemented?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:34.25,2:02:35.87,chinese,,0,0,0,,内部又是如何实现的呢？
Dialogue: 0,2:02:35.87,2:02:37.19,english,,0,0,0,,Well, this one's a bit long.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:35.87,2:02:37.19,chinese,,0,0,0,,啊，这个有点长。
Dialogue: 0,2:02:37.19,2:02:40.08,english,,0,0,0,,But on the left here is Listen for Keyboard.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:37.19,2:02:40.08,chinese,,0,0,0,,左侧是 "监听键盘"。
Dialogue: 0,2:02:40.08,2:02:47.42,english,,0,0,0,,So this pink puzzle piece, Listen for Keyboard, first checks If the Key Up Arrow is Pressed, question mark,
Dialogue: 0,2:02:40.08,2:02:47.42,chinese,,0,0,0,,这块粉色拼图 "监听键盘"，首先要检查 "是否按下上箭头键"，
Dialogue: 0,2:02:47.42,2:02:50.57,english,,0,0,0,,Boolean expression in a conditional, Change y By 1.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:47.42,2:02:50.57,chinese,,0,0,0,,如果满足，就让 y 增加 1。
Dialogue: 0,2:02:50.57,2:02:52.04,english,,0,0,0,,That means, move it up 1.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:50.57,2:02:52.04,chinese,,0,0,0,,也就是说把徽章上移 1 个像素。
Dialogue: 0,2:02:52.04,2:02:59.54,english,,0,0,0,,Else If the Key Down Arrow is Pressed, then Change y by -1, and similar for Left Arrow, similar for Right Arrow.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:52.04,2:02:59.54,chinese,,0,0,0,,否则，如果按下箭头键，则将 y-1，左右箭头的操作类似。
Dialogue: 0,2:02:59.54,2:03:04.31,english,,0,0,0,,And even though there's not a loop in this pink function, there is where I'm using it.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:59.54,2:03:04.31,chinese,,0,0,0,,尽管在这个粉红色函数中没有循环，但在使用它的地方却有循环。
Dialogue: 0,2:03:04.31,2:03:06.86,english,,0,0,0,,So it's constantly being asked again and again.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:04.31,2:03:06.86,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以这个条件语句在反复被检查。
Dialogue: 0,2:03:06.86,2:03:08.42,english,,0,0,0,,How about feeling for walls?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:06.86,2:03:08.42,chinese,,0,0,0,,什么是墙壁感知？
Dialogue: 0,2:03:08.42,2:03:13.97,english,,0,0,0,,Well, over here to the right-- it's a little cut off-- but here you have, If Touching Left Wall,
Dialogue: 0,2:03:08.42,2:03:13.97,chinese,,0,0,0,,在这个右边，有点太长了，它是说如果接触到左墙...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:13.97,2:03:15.26,english,,0,0,0,,Change x by 1.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:13.97,2:03:15.26,chinese,,0,0,0,,就让 x 加一。
Dialogue: 0,2:03:15.26,2:03:17.20,english,,0,0,0,,So if you hit the wall, it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:15.26,2:03:17.20,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以如果它碰到了墙，那就太晚了。
Dialogue: 0,2:03:17.20,2:03:18.95,english,,0,0,0,,You're kind of blowing through it already.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:17.20,2:03:18.95,chinese,,0,0,0,,你已经穿过它了。
Dialogue: 0,2:03:18.95,2:03:23.00,english,,0,0,0,,So I want to move it back one pixel so it's no longer touching that wall.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:18.95,2:03:23.00,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以我想让它后退一个像素，这样它就不再撞到那堵墙了。
Dialogue: 0,2:03:23.00,2:03:28.22,english,,0,0,0,,Similarly, if it's touching the right wall, I want to back it up one pixel so it's no longer touching that wall.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:23.00,2:03:28.22,chinese,,0,0,0,,同样地，如果它碰到了右墙，我也让它后退一个像素，就不再撞到那堵墙了。
Dialogue: 0,2:03:28.22,2:03:33.11,english,,0,0,0,,So it's kind of like bouncing off ever so slightly so that it doesn't slip through that actual wall.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:28.22,2:03:33.11,chinese,,0,0,0,,所以它就像是微微地反弹，这样就不会从真正的墙壁滑过。
Dialogue: 0,2:03:33.11,2:03:34.34,english,,0,0,0,,And what are those walls?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:33.11,2:03:34.34,chinese,,0,0,0,,那些墙是什么？
Dialogue: 0,2:03:34.34,2:03:41.79,english,,0,0,0,,Well, notice down here, it's just a simple sprite with a black line that I've oriented vertically instead of horizontally.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:34.34,2:03:41.79,chinese,,0,0,0,,注意看下面，这只是一个简单的精灵，带有一条黑线，我把它的方向改为垂直而不是水平。
Dialogue: 0,2:03:41.79,2:03:45.23,english,,0,0,0,,And that's just so that I can ask questions of these other two sprites.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:41.79,2:03:45.23,chinese,,0,0,0,,这样我就可以询问 logo 和两面墙的关系了。
